hadiths[325]{hadithnumber,text}:
1721,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aqraa bin Haabis (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya hajj her saal hai ya eik hi baar? aapney farmaya : ''nahin ! eik hi baar hai aur jo us se ziyada karey to wo nafl hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke raawi hadees (Abu-Sanaan) ye Abu-Sanaan Dauli hain. Abdul-Jaleel bin Humaid aur Sulaiman bin Kasir sabhi Zohri se (Abu-Sanaan) zikr kartey hain. sirf Aqeel ''sanaan'' kehtey hain. (Abu-Sanaan nahin kehtey.)
1722,"Hazrat Abu Waqid Al Yasee (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap apni azwaaj (biwiyon) se Hijjatul Wadaa mein farma rahey they : ''hajj bas yehi hai, phir (ghar ki) chataaiyon ko lazim pakadna hai.''"
1723,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi musalman khatoon ko apney kisi mahram ke sath ke baghair eik raat ka safar bhi halal nahin hai.''
1724,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo aurat Allah aur aakhirat ke din par emaan rakhti hai, us ke liye halal nahin ke eik din aur raat ka safar karey.'' aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kiya. (yani uska mahram ke baghair safar karna haram hai) Nufaili ne (عن مالك) ke bajaey tahdis ki saraahat kartey huey (حدثنا مالك) kaha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Nufaili aur Qaanabi ne (sanad mein Saeed bin abi Saeed ke baad) (عن أبيه) nahin kaha . isi ke sath ibne-Wahab aur Usman bin umr bhi Janab Malik se aisey hi riwayat kartey hain jaisey ke Qaanabi ne kaha hai. (عن أبيه ke baghair.)"
1725,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : . ... . aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kiya, magar (Barida) ka lafz kaha. (yani kisi musalman aurat ko apney mahram ke baghair eik bareed ka safar bhi halal nahin.)"
1726,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo aurat jo Allah aur aakhirat par emaan rakhti ho uskey liye halal nahin ke apney baap , bhai , khawind , bete ya kisi aur mahram ke sath ke baghair teen din ya us se ziyada ka safar karey.''"
1727,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''aurat apney mahram ke baghair teen din ka (bhi) safar na karey.''
1728,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke wo apni londi ko apney sath bitha kar ley jatey they. uska naam Safiya tha. wo unke sath Makka ka safar karti thi.
1729,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein ''saruraa'' nahin hai.'' ( koi shakhs bawajood taqat hone ke hajj kerney se aeraz kar ley (bache).)
1730,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke log hajj ko aatey magar zaade-raah sath na latey they. ... Abu-Masood ne kaha ke ehale-Yamen ya kuch ehale-Yamen hajj ke liye aatey magar zaade-raah sath na latey . ... . aur kehtey ke ham mutawakkil log hain. isliye Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : (وَتَزَوَّدُوا فَإِنَّ خَيْرَ الزَّادِ التَّقْوَى) ''zaade-raah (yani safar ka kharch) sath lekar chalo isliye ke behtareen tosha, taqwa (sawal se bachna) hai.''"
1731,Janab Mujahid bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aayat kareema (لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَنْ تَبْتَغُوا فَضْلًا مِنْ رَبِّكُم) ''tum par koi gunah nahin ke apney Rab ka fazal talash karo.''padhi aur farmaya : kuchh log Mina mein tijarat na kartey they to unhen hukm diya gaya ke jab Arafat se wapis lauten to tijarat kar saktey hain.
1732,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo hajj karna chahey to chahiye ke jald hi kar ley.''
1733,Janab Abu-Umama Taimi bayan kartey hain ke main safar mein kiraaey ki sawariyan chalaya karta tha to baaz logon ne mujh se kaha : ''tera hajj nahin hai.'' main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se mila aur un se puchha ke aey Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main safar hajj mein kiraaey par sawariyan chalata hun aur kuchh log mujhey kehtey hain ke tera hajj nahin hai. to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne jawab diya : kya tum ehram nahin baandhtey ho aur talbiya nahin padhtey ho? kya Baitullah ka tawaf nahin kartey ho? Arafat se nahin laut'tey ho? aur jamaraat ko kankariyaan nahin maartey ho? maine kaha : kyon nahin (sab kuchh karta hun) unhoney farmaya : bila-shuba tera hajj (sahih) hai. eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya tha aur usney bilkul yehi sawal kiya tha jaisey ke tum ne mujh se kiya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho rahey aur usko jawab nahin diya tha yahan tak ke ye aayat kareema nazil hui (لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَنْ تَبْتَغُوا فَضْلًا مِنْ رَبِّكُم) ''tum par koi gunah (aur harj) nahin ke apney Rab ka fazal talash karo.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko bula bheja aur us par ye aayat padhi aur farmaya : tera hajj (sahih) hai.
1734,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke log pehley (Islam se pahle) hajj ke dino mein minaa, Arafat ,sooq zil mijaaz aur hajj ke dinon mein kharida aur farokht kiya kartey they. (iIslam laney ke baad) unhoney ehram baandhey huey kharida aur farokht mein harj samjha tu Allah taala ne ye aayat utaari (لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَنْ تَبْتَغُوا فَضْلًا مِنْ رَبِّكُم فِي مَوَاسِمِ الْحَجِّ) ''tum par koi harj ya gunah nahin ke ''ayyaame-hajj'' main Allah ka fazal talash karo.'' Ubaid bin Umair ne bayan kiya ke wo (في مواسم الحج) ke izafe ke sath , mushaf (kitab) mein padha kartey they."
1735,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke log pehley zamaney mein haj ke dauran mein kharida aur farokht kiya kartey they. aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. ... (مواسم الحج) tak.
1736,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maqame-rauhaa par they ke aap ko eik qafile waley miley . aapney unhen salam kaha aur puchha : kaun log ho? unhoney kaha : ham musalman hain. unhoney puchha : aap kaun log hain? Sahaba (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne kaha : ye Allah taala ke Rasool hain. to eik aurat ne jaldi se apney bachchey ko bazu se pakda aur apney hodaj se bahir nikala aur boli : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya iskey liye haj hai? aapney farmaya : ''haan ! aur terey liye ajr hai.''
1737,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale-Madina ke liye ''Zul-Hulaifa'' (mojuda آبارعلی) , ahle-Sham ke liye ''Johfa''  ehle-Najad ke liye ''قرن المنازل'' ke maqamat mutayyan (tey) farmaai they. aur mujhey ye khabar bhi pahunchi hai ke aapney ehale-Yaman ke liye ''yalamlam'' mutayyan kiya tha."
1738,"Hammad , Amr bin Dinar sey, wo Taaus sey, wo ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se. ... . aur ibne Taaus (Abdullah) apney baap Taaus se (wo ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey) riwayat kartey hain. un dono (Amr bin Dinar aur Abdullah bin Taaoos) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meeqaat (maqamate ehraam) muqarrar farmaai they. un dono mein se eik ne kaha ke ehale-Yaman ke liye (yalamlam) aur doosrey ne kaha (العلم). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye maqamat in (mazkura) jagahon ke rehney walon ke liye hain aur dusri jagahon ke un logon ke liye bhi jo yahan se guzren jo ke hajj aur Umra ki niyat rakhtey hon aur jo un se warey (makka ki janib) muqeem (niwasi) hon.'' ibne Taaus ne kaha . ... . wo wahin se ehram baandhen jahan se wo safar shuru keren yahan tak ke ehale-makka apney shehar aur ghar hi se ehram baandh kar niklen."
1739,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale-Iraq ke liye ''zaatur-Riqaa '' ka maqam mutayyan (tey) farmaya tha. (ehraam ke liye.)"
1740,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale-mashriq ke liye maqam ''aqeeq'' muqarrar farmaya tha.
1741,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney masjide aqsaa se masjid haram tak hajj ya Umerey ka ehram baandha , uskey agley pichley sab gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey. ya farmaya : uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee.'' Abdullah ( ibne-Abdur-Rehman bin Yahnas) ko shak hua hai ke maloom nahin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dono se kaunn si baat kahi thi. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain : Allah taala Wakee par rehmat farmaai , unhoney baitul-Maqdis se Makka ke liye ehram baandha."
1742,"Janab Haris bin Amr Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap Mina ya Arafat mein they. logon ne aap ko gher rakha tha. badwi log aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aatey they, jab aap ka chehra anwar dekhtey to kehtey : ''ye to Mubarak chehra hai.'' Haris bayan kartey hain ke aapney ehle-Iraq ke liye maqam ''zaat arq'' ko meeqaat muqarrar farmaya."
1743,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anha) ( zauja abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu)) ne shajra ke maqam par Muhammad bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''usey chahiye ke ghusl karkey ehram baandh ley.''
1744,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haiz aur nifaas wali aurten jab meeqaat par pahunchein to ghusl karkey ehram baandh lein aur hajj ke tamam aamaal sar anjam den , siwaye Baitullah ke tawaf ke .'' abu-Ma'mar ki riwayat mein hai, yahan tak ke wo paak ho jaeyn .'' Muhammad bin Esa ki riwayat mein Ikrima aur Mujahid ka zikr nahin hai balke (us ki sanad ( '' Ata an ibne-Abbas'' hai aisey hi ibn Esa ki riwayat mein) كلها (ka lafz nahin aaya balke yun kaha ( المناسك إلا الطواف بالبيت ("
1745,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aap ke ehram baandhney ke waqt , ehram se pehley khushbu lagaya karti thi aur aisey hi ehram kholney ke baad , Baitullah ka tawaf kerney se pehley ."
1746,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, farmati hain ke goya main kastoori ki us chamak ko dekh rahi hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mang mein lagi hoti jabke aap ehram mein hotey ."
1747,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko talbiya pukartey huey suna jabke aap apney sar ke baal jamaey huey they.
1748,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( Asl (ke sath apney baal chipkaaey huey they.
1749,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hudebiya ke saal qurbani ke janwer ( sath ( ley gaey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki un qurbaniyon main eik oont wo bhi tha jo abu-Jahal ka tha. ... . uski naak mein chaandi ka chhalla pada hua tha. ... ibne-minhaal ne kaha : soney ka chhalla pada hua tha. Nufaili ne izafa kya ke aap usey mushrikon ko jalaney ke liye ley gaey they. (ke unke sardar ka oont Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qabzey mein hai.)
1750,ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatil-wadaa mein aal Muhammad ki taraf se eik gaey zibeh ki thi.
1751,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni azwaaj ki taraf sey, jinhon ne Umra kya tha, eik gaey zibeh ki thi."
1752,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz zal-Hulaifa maqam par padhi . phir aapney apni qurbani ki oontni talab ki aur uskey kohan ki daain janib cheer lagaya aur uska khoon wahin chipad diya aur uskey galey mein do jooton ka haar bhi dal diya. phir aap ki sawari laee gaee . jab aap us par beth gaey aur wo aap ko lekar Beda maidan ke qarib pahunchi to aapney hajj ka talbiya pukara.
1753,"Shoba ne ye hadees abul-Waleed ke ham-maani riwayat ki, kaha ke phir aapney apney haath se khoon chipda . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : Hammam ki riwayat mein hai ke aapney apni ungli se khoon chipda . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye riwayat ehle-Basra ke tafarrudaat (yaktaiyat) mein se hai."
1754,"Miswar bin Makhrima aur Marwan (bin Hakam ( bayan kartey hain ke Hudebiya ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley , jab aap zal-Hulaifa ke maqam par pahunchey to aapney qurbani ko qalada pehnaya , uska ashaar kya aur ehram baandha ."
1755,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bakriyan bator hudi (Haram ki taraf ( bhijwaaeen aur unki gardanon mein qaladey daley .
1756,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik bada oont bator hudi ( Haram ki taraf ( bhijwaya. unhen uskey teen so Dinar pesh kiye gaey ..... to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine eik umda oont hudi kya hai aur mujhey uskey teen so Dinar diye ja rahey hain to kya main usey bech kar uski qeemat ke doosrey oont ley lun ? aapney farmaya : '' nahin, usey hi nahar ( zibeh ( karo.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye isliye tha ke wo usey ashaar kar chukey they."
1757,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbani ke oont ke haar ki rassiyan apney haathon se batin, phir aapney unka ashaar kya aur unke galey mein qalada dala, phir usey Baitullah ki janib rawana kar diya aur khud Madina mein muqeem rahey to jo chizen aap ke liye halal thin (usi tarah halal hi rahin) kuch bhi haram na hua."
1758,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina se hudi bheja kartey they. mein unke qaladon ki rassiyan bataa karti thi aur phir aap kisi chiz se ijtinab na kartey jis se ke mahram ijtinab karta hai.
1759,"ummul-momenin ( Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hudi bhijwaai aur maine oon se jo hamarey yahan thi , uskey qaladon ki rassiyan batin, phir aap hamarey yahan usi tarah halal hi rahey . apney ehle ke paas aatey jaisey ke koi aam aadmi aata hai."
1760,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko dekha ke wo apni qurbani ka oont haankey ja raha tha (aur khud pedal chal raha tha ( to aapney us se farmaya : '' us par Sawar ho jao .'' usney kaha : ye qurbani ke liye hai. aapney farmaya : '' us par Sawar ho jao . ... tum par afsos ! '' aapney ye ( afsos ka lafz (dusri ya teesri baar mein farmaya.
1761,"Janab abu-Zubair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se qurbani ke janwer par sawari ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farma rahey they : ''jab tum majboor ho jao to ( ehsan ke sath aur) maroof andaz se us par sawari karo yahan tak ke tumhen koi aur sawari mil jaey.''"
1762,"Hazrat Naajiya Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke haath apni qurbani bhijwaai aur unhen farmaya : ''agar un mein se koi janwer halak honey lagey to usey nahar kar dena , uskey jootey ko uskey khoon se rang dena , phir usey logon ke liye chhod dena .''"
1763,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne falan Aslami ko bheja aur uskey sath atthaara oont qurbani ke bhijwaaye. wo kehney laga : farmaiye agar un mein se koi apney paon ghaseetney lagey (chalney se laachaar ho jaey aur thak jaey to?) aapney farmaya : ''usey nahar kar dena , uskey jooton ko khoon se chipad kar uski kohan par nishan laga dena aur tum ya tumharey sathiyon mein se koi us se na khaye .'' hadees ke lafz ( من أصحابك) they ya (من أهل رفقتك ( they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees mein ye jumla (ولا تأكل منها أنت ولا أحدٍ من أهلِ رفقتِكَ) munfarid hai aur Abdul-Waris ki riwayat mein) ثم اضربها ( ki bajaey (اجعله على صفحتها) aaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine abu-Salma ( Musa bin Ismael Munqari ( se suna, wo kehtey they ke jab tum ne hadees ki sanad aur uskey maani sahih aur durust taur par bayan kar diye to kafi hai) alfaz badalney se koi farq nahin padta , yani riwayat bil-maana jayez hai. ("
1764,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab apney oont nahar kiye to tees oont apney haath se nahar kiye aur baqi ke mutalliq mujhey hukm farmaya aur maine unhen nahar kya.
1765,Hazrat Abdullah bin Qart (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tabarak w taala ke yahan sab se badh kar azmat wala din Yomun-Nehar ( das zul-hijja ( uskey baad یوم الق (11 zul-hijja ( hai.'' Esa ne Saur se naqal kya ke ye doosra din hota hai. aur bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney paanch ya chhe oontniyaan laee gaeen to wo aap ke qarib honey lagen ke aap usi se ibtida (shuruat) karen. jab wo sab ( nahar ho gaeen aur) pahluon ke bal gir padin to aapney aahista se kuch farmaya jo main na samajh saka . maine ( sath walon sey) puchha ke aapney kya farmaya hai? to bataya ke ''jo chahey ( gosht ( kaat ley jaey.''
1766,"Hazrat Arfa bin Haris Kandi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Hajjatil-wadaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan hazir tha ke qurbani ki oontniyaan laee gaeen . aapney farmaya : '' abul-Hasan ( Ali ( ko bulao .'' chunanche unhen aap ke liye bulaya gaya , to aapney un se farmaya : '' barchhey ko nichey se pakdo .'' aur khud aapney uskey ooper se pakda , phir aap dono ne usey ( oontniyon ke nahar kerney mein) chalaya . jab aap farigh ho gaey to apney khachar par Sawar huey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi apney sath bitha liya ."
1767,"Janab abu-Khalid Ahmar, ibne-Juraij sey, wo abu-Zubair se aur wo Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain. ... aur) ibne-Juraij ne kaha : ( mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin Sabit ne khabar di. ... . ke '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba oont ko '' nahar ''kya kartey they jabkey uska baayan paon bandha hota aur wo baqi teen paon par khada hota ."
1768,"Janab Ziyad bin Jubair kehtey hain ke main Mina mein Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tha ke wo eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey aur wo apni oontni ko nahar karna chaha raha tha jabkey wo bethi hui thi. to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : ''usey khadi karo, ( eik ( paon bandha hua ho, yehi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat hai.''"
1769,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke main aap ke oonton ke paas khada ho jaun (jabkey wo nahar kiye ja rahey they (aur unke chamdey aur jhol taqseem kar dun . qassaab ko un mein se koi cheez na dun . unhoney bataya ke qassaab ki mazduri ham apney paas se diya kartey they.
1770,"Hazrat Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : aey Abul-Abbaas ! mujhey tajjub hai ke as-haabe-Rasul, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehram ke baarey mein ikhtilaf kartey hain ke aapney kis waqt ehram baandha tha. unhoney kaha : main is baarey mein sab se ziyada ba-khabar hun. darasal aapney chunkey eik hi hajj kya hai to is wajeh se ikhtilaf hua hai. aap hajj ki niyat se rawana huey . jab aapney apni masjid mein yani zal-Hulaifa mein do rakatein padh lin to aapney apni usi majlis mein niyat farma li aur un do rakaaton se farigh honey ke baad hajj ka talbiya kaha . pas kuch logon ne us waqt sun liya aur usey yaad rakha . phir aap apni sawari par Sawar ho gaey . jab aap ki oontni aap ko lekar khadi hui to aapney talbiya kaha, kuch logon ne usko paya . dar-haqeeqat log giroh dar giroh aap ke paas aa rahey they to jinhon ne aap ko oontni par bethey huey talbiya pukartey suna, unhoney yehi samjha ke aapney oontni par bethney ke baad , jab wo khadi hui hai, talbiya kaha hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chal diye aur jab maidane-Beda ki bulandi par pahunchey to aapney talbiya kaha. kuch logon ne usko paya to unhoney kaha ke aapney Beda ki bulandi par pahunch kar talbiya kaha . (Saeed ne kaha) qasam Allah ki ! aapney apni jaey Namaz hi par talbiya kaha tha. phir jab aap ki oontni aap ko lekar khadi hui to talbiya kaha . aur jab maidan Beda ki bulandi par pahunchi to aapney talbiya kaha . Saeed bin Jubair ne kaha ke jo log Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke bayan par amal paira hain wo apni do rakaaton ke baad jaey Namaz hi se talbiya shuru kar detey hain."
1771,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : tum log us maidan Beda ke baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq ghalat kehtey ho. aapney to masjid hi ke paas talbiya pukarna shuru kar diya tha. ... yani zal-Hulaifa ki masjid ke paas se.
1772,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Juraij kehtey hain ke unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : aey Abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main aap ko chaar kaam kartey dekhta hun, aap ka koi sathi ye nahin karta. unhoney kaha : aey ibne-Juraij ! wo kya hain? unhoney kaha : maine aap ko dekha hai ke aap ( daurane tawaf mein) Baitullah ke sirf do konon ( يمانيين) (Hajare-Aswad aur rukne-yamaani) ko haath lagatey hain aur aap ko dekha hai ke aap aisey chamdey ki jooti pehantey hain jis par baal nahin hotey . aur aap ko dekha hai ke zard rang istimal kartey hain. (kapdon mein ya baalon mein bataur khizaab ke) aur maine aap ko dekha hai ke jab aap Makka mein hon to log chaand dekhtey hi ehram baandh letey hain magar aap aath-win zul-hijja ko ehram baandhtey hain. Hazrat Abdullah bin umr ne jawab diya : jahan tak (dauran tawaf mein) arkaan ko chhuney ka talluq hai to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap sirf dono yamaani arkaan hi ko chhotey they. (Hajare-Aswad aur rukn yamaani ko.) aur be-baal chamdey ke jootey. .... to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap ka joota aisey chamdey ka hota tha jis par baal na hotey they aur aap us mein wuzu ( bhi) kar liya kartey they to main aisey hi jootey pehanna pasand karta hun. aur raha zard rang . . . . . to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap us se rangtey they, lihaza main bhi us se rangnaa pasand karta hun. raha ehram aur talbiya . ... to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nahin dekha ke aap apni sawari ke khadi honey se pehley talbiya pukartey hon."
1773,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madiney mein Zohar ki Namaz chaar rakaat ada farmae aur Zul-Hulaifa mein Asr ki do rakaten padhein aur yahin raat guzari yahan tak ke subh ho gaee . phir jab aap apni sawari par Sawar huey aur wo aap ko lekar sidhi khadi ho gaee to aapney talbiya pukara .
1774,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padhi , phir apni sawari par Sawar huey aur jab maidane Beda ke reteele tiley ki bulandi par pahunchey to aapney talbiya pukara ."
1775,Janab Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab (faraa') ki raah ikhtiyar kartey to us waqt talbiya pukarna shuru kartey jab aap ki sawari aap ko lekar sidhi khadi ho jati . aur jab ahad ki raah se chalney lagtey to us waqt talbiya kehtey jab Beda ke tiley par chadhtey .
1776,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke (Umme-Hakeem) Zabaa binte Zuber bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main hajj ka irada rakhti hun to (kya) shart kar lun? farmaya : ''haan !'' kehney lagin : to kaisey kahun? farmaya : ''kaho :  لبيك ! اللهم لبيك . ... . main raastey mein wahin halal ho jaun gi jahan to mujhey rok lega .''
1777,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) riwayat karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajje afrad kiya tha.
1778,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan farmati hain ke zul-hijja ka chaand aaney par ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley. jab Zul-Hulaifa maqam par aaye to aapney farmaya : ''jo hajj ka ehram baandhnaa chahta hai baandh ley aur jo chahey Umerey ki niyat kar ley.'' . ... Musa bin Ismael ne Wuhaib ki riwayat mein bayan kiya ke . ... (aapney farmaya :) ''maine agar qurbani sath na li hoti to Umerey ka ehram baandhta.'' aur Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat mein kaha : . ... . ''aur main hajj ka ehram baandh raha hun kyonkey merey sath qurbani hai.'' aagey riwayat bayan karney mein sab raawi muttafiq hain. (Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke) main un afrad mein se thi jinhonne Umerey ka ehram baandha , phir raastey main eik jagah mujhey haiz shuru ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye aur main ro rahi thi. aapney puchha : kyon ro rahi ho? maine kaha : main chahti hun ke is saal na aai hoti ( to achchhaa tha). aapney farmaya : ''apna Umra chhod do , apney baal khol lo aur kanghi kar lo.'' Musa ne kaha : ''aur hajj ki niyat kar lo . ... .'' aur Sulaiman ne kaha . ... ''aur isi tarah karo jaisey ke musalman apney hajj mein kartey hain.'' yani jab (hajj sey) wapsi ki raat aai , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman ( ibne-abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) yani Aaysha ke bhai ( ko hukm diya, to wo unhen tan'eem ley gaey . . . . . Musa ne mazeed kaha . ... isliye unhoney Umerey ka ehram baandha. yani apney pehley Umerey ke badley , phir Baitullah ka tawaf kiya.yani  Allah ne unka Umra aur hajj pura kara diya. Hisham kehtey hain. ... is soorat mein koi hudi ( fidya waghaira) na hua. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Musa ne Hammad bin Salma ki riwayat mein mazeed kaha : phir jab Bat'haa ki raat aai (yani Mina mein iqaamat ki raat ( to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) paak ho gaee thin."
1779,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham Hijjatul-wadaa ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley. ham mein se baaz ne Umerey ka ehram baandha , baaz ne hajj aur Umerey ka aur baaz ne sirf hajj ka jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj ka ehram baandha tha. to jinhon ne hajj ya hajj aur Umerey ka ehram baandha tha wo qurbani ke din (yaumun-nahar 10 zul-hijja ( tak halal na huey."
1780,Malik ne Abu Aswad se apni sanad se usi ke jaise bayan kiya aur ye mazeed kaha : aur jinhon ne Umerey ka ehram baandha tha wo halal ho gaey.
1781,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham Hijjatul-wadaa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley . ham ne Umerey ka ehram baandha. phir aapney farmaya : ''jiskey sath hudi (Qurbani) hai wo Umerey ke sath hajj ka talbiya bhi kahe, aur wo halal nahin hoga yahan tak ke un dono se farigh ho.'' so main Makka aai to haiz ki keyfiyat mein thi. maine Baitullah ka tawaf nahin kiya aur na Safa Marwa ki saee ki . maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uski shikayat ki, to aapney farmaya : ''apna sar khol lo , kanghi kar lo aur hajj ka ehram baandh lo aur Umra chhod do.'' farmati hain : chunanche maine aisey hi kiya. phir jab ham ne hajj pura kar liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey (merey bhai) Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tan'eem bheja aur maine Umra kiya. aur aapney farmaya : ''ye terey us Umerey ke badley hai.'' wo bayan karti hain ke (makka pahunchney ke baad) jin logon ne Umerey ka ehram baandh rakha tha unhoney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki aur phir halal ho gaey. un logon ne meena se wapsi ke baad hajj ke liye eik aur tawaf kiya (tawafe-ifaaza ziyada) magar jin logon ne hajj aur Umerey ka ikhattey ehram baandha tha (Hajje-Qiraana ka ( to unhoney sirf eik hi tawaf kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke usey Ibrahim bin Saad aur Maamer ne ibne-Shahab se usi ki manind riwayat kiya hai. un logon ne Umre ka ehram baandhney walon ya hajj aur Umre ka ikhatta ehram baandhney walon ke tawaf ka zikr nahin kiya."
1782,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham ne hajj ka talbiya kaha yahan tak ke jab ham maqame sarf par pahunchey to mujhey haiz aa gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye to main ro rahi thi. aapney puchha : '' Aaisha ! kyon ro rahi ho ?'' maine kaha : mujhey haiz aa gaya hai. kash ! main hajj ke liye na aai hoti . aapney farmaya : ''Subhanallah ! ye to aisi chiz hai jo Allah ne Adam ki betiyon par likh di hai.''  tab aapney farmaya : ''hajj ke tamam aamaal purey karo, sirf Baitullah ka tawaf na karna.'' chunanche jab ham Makka mein dakhil huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo apney is ehram ko Umerey ka banana chahey bana ley, siwaye uskey jiskey paas qurbani ho.'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke din apni azwaaj (biwiyon) ki taraf se gayen zibeh kin aur jab Bat'haa ki raat aai aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) paak ho gaeen to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya merey sath wali hajj aur Umra karkey jaeyngi aur main sirf hajj ke sath lautoon gi? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko hukm diya wo usey tan'eem ley gaey aur us ( Aaisha ( ne Umerey ka talbiya kaha."
1783,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley, ham sirf hajj samajh rahey they. magar jab ham Makka pahunchey aur Baitullah ka tawaf kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke jo shakhs qurbani sath nahin laya wo halal ho jaey. chunanche wo log jo qurbaaniyaan sath nahin laye they, halal ho gaey."
1784,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mujhey is baat ki khabar pehley hoti jiski baad mein hui hai to main qurbani sath lekar na aata. Muhammad bin Yahya ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke sheikh ne ye bhi kaha : ''aur main Umerey ke baad halal honey walon ke sath halal ho jata.'' kaha : aap ka irada tha ke sab log eik hi haal par hon.
1785,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sirf hajj (hajje-afrad) ki niyat se chaley aur Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne Umerey ka ehram baandha yahan tak ke jab maqame-sarf mein pahunchin to unhen haiz aa gaya. phir jab ham Makka aaye aur kaabay ka tawaf kiya aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen hukm diya ke ham mein se jis jiskey paas qurbani nahin hai wo halal ho jaey. ham ne kaha : halal hona kaisa? aapney farmaya : ''puri tarah se halal hona . ... '' chunanche ham apni azwaaj (biwiyon) se ham bistar bhi huye, khushbuein lagain aur apney aam kapdey pehan liye . halanke hamarey aur Arfa janey ke darmiyan sirf chaar raaten baqi thin . phir ham ne aathwein taareekh ko ehram baandha , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaye to dekha ke ro rahi hain. aapney puchha : ''tumhen kya hua hai? '' kehney lagin ke mujhey haiz aa gaya hai. log halal huye, mein halal nahin hui, aur na Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur ab wo hajj ke liye ja rahey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye mamla tu Allah ne Adam ki betiyon par likh diya hai. tum ghusl kar lo aur hajj ke liye ehram baandh lo.'' chunanche unhoney aisey hi kiya aur hajj ke tamam maqamat par thehren yahan tak ke jab paak ho gaeen to Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki. phir aapney farmaya : ''tum apney hajj aur Umerey sab se halal ho gaee ho.'' kehney lagin : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey dil mein hasrat hai ke maine jab hajj kiya to (ibtida (shuruat) mein) tawaf nahin kar saki . aapney farmaya : ''aey Abdur-Rehman unko ley jao aur tan'eem se Umra kara lao .'' aur ye hasba ki raat thi. (yani dinon (din) tashreeq ke baad jis raat Madina ki taraf wapsi ke liye Bat'haa mein padaaw dala gaya tha.)"
1786,"Abu-Zubair kehtey hain ke unhoney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaye aur us qissey ka kuchh hissey bayan kiya. ... aur) أهلي بالحج ( ''hajj ke liye ehram baandh lo.'' ke baad ye farmaya : ''phir hajj karo aur wo sab kuchh karo jaisey haaji karta hai. sirf Baitullah ka tawaf na karna aur Namaz na padhna.''"
1787,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khalis hajj ka ehram baandha. is mein kisi cheez ka ikhtilaat (ghaal-mel) na tha. phir zil-hijja ki chaar raaten guzar janey ke baad ham Makka pahunchey. ham ne tawaf aur saee ki . phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen halal honey ka hukm dey diya aur farmaya : ''agar merey sath qurbani na hoti to main bhi halal ho jata.'' phir Hazrat Suraqa bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamara ye tamatto (hajj ke sath Umra karna) isi saal ke liye hai ya hamesha hamesha ke liye? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' balke hamesha hamesha ke liye hai. Auzaai kehtey hain ke maine Ata bin Abi Ribah ko ye hadees bayan kartey suna magar main yaad na rakh saka yahan tak ke ibne-Juraij se mila to unhoney mujhey yaad karaai.
1788,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba (makka) pahunchey jabkey zil-Hijja ki chaar raaten guzar chuki thin. jab unhoney Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey Umra bana lo , siwaye uskey jiskey sath qurbani ho.'' so jab aathwein taareekh aai to un logon ne hajj ka ehram baandha aur phir qurbani waley din (das zil-hijja ko) ye log Makka aaye aur Baitullah ka tawaf kiya magar Safa Marwa ki saee nahin ki."
1789,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ne hajj ka ehram baandha. us din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke alawa kisi ke paas qurbani na thi. aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen se aaye they aur wo apney sath qurbaaniyaan laye they. isliye unhoney is tarah niyat ki thi : main usi tarah ehram baandhta hun jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram baandha hai. aur aapney apney Sahaba (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko hukm diya tha ke apney ehram ko Umra ka ehram bana lon, tawaf keren (safa Marwa ki saee bhi karen) phir baal katwaa kar halal ho jaeyn, siwaye uskey jiskey sath qurbani ho. kuchh logon ne kaha : to kya ham mina ko is haalat mein jaeyngey ke hamarey aa'zaaey-tanaasul mani tapkaa rahey hon gey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pahunchi to aapney farmaya : ''agar mujhey ye baat pehley maloom hoti jo baad mein maloom hui to main qurbani sath na lata aur agar merey sath qurbani na hoti to main  (bhi) halal ho jata.''"
1790,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''ye Umra hai ham ne iska fayda hasil kiya hai, so jiskey sath qurbani na ho wo halal ho jaey, puri tarah halal hona . aur qiyamat tak ke liye Umra hajj mein dakhil ho gaya hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : ye riwayat munkir hai. ye sirf ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka qaul hai."
1791,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jab aadmi ne hajj ka ehram baandha phir Makka aaya, Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar li to wo halal ho gaya aur ye Umra hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : is hadees ko ibne-Juraij ne eik shakhs ke wastey se Ata se yun riwayat kiya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab sirf hajj ka talbiya kehtey huey (makkey mein) dakhil huey. isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko Umra bana diya."
1792,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj ka talbiya kaha. jab Makka tashrif laye aur Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar li . ... ibn Shaukar ne kaha . ... . aur aapney apney baal nahin katarwaaey . ... . phir ibn Shaukar aur Ahmed bin Munee' dono ne kaha . ... . aur aap apni qurbani ki wajeh se halal nahin huey. (lekin) jin logon ke sath qurbani nahin thi , unhen hukm diya ke tawaf aur saee ke baad baal katarwaa kar halal ho jaeyn . ibn Munee' ki riwayat mein izafa hai : ya baal mundwaa kar halal ho jaeyn."
1793,Saeed bin Musaiyab se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik shakhs Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur gawahi di ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aap ke marzul-maut mein suna hai ke aap hajj se pehley Umra kerney se mana farmatey they.
1794,"Hazrat Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : kya aap log jantey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne falan falan kaam se mana farmaya hai aur chheetey ki khaal par Sawar honey (baithney) se bhi mana farmaya hai? unhoney kaha : haan ! unhoney kaha : aap log ye bhi jantey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj aur Umerey ko milaaney se bhi mana kiya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, ye baat ham nahin jantey. Muawiya ne kaha : ye hai to un (mamnoo chizon) hi ke sath magar aap log bhool rahey hain.''"
1795,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna ke aap hajj aur Umerey ka talbiya ikhattey padhtey huey keh rahey they : (لبيك عمرة وحجا ، لبيك عمرة وحجا).
1796,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zul-Hulaifa ke maqam par raat guzari yahan tak ke subh ho gaee . phir aap (zohar ke baad) apni sawari par Sawar huey yahan tak ke jab wo aap ko lekar maidane-Beda mein sidhi khadi hui to aapney Allah ki hamd , tasbih aur takbir pukaari. phir hajj aur Umerey ka talbiya kaha. aur logon ne bhi un dono ka talbiya kaha. phir jab ham Makka pahunchey to aapney logon ko hukm diya to wo halal ho gaey. (un logon ko jinkey paas qurbaaniyaan nahin thin) yahan tak ke jab aathwin taareekh aai to unhoney hajj ka ehram baandha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath se saat oontniyaan nahar (qurbaan) kin, is haal mein ke wo khadi hui thin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) is riwayat mein is baat mein munfarid (alag) hain ke unhoney ''Allah ki hamd , tasbih aur takbir kahi , phir hajj ka talbiya kaha.''"
1797,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Yamen ka wali bana kar bheja to main unke sath tha. us khidmat ke siley mein mujhey chand auqiya (sona) bhi mila tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab Yamen se wapsi ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se miley to wo kehtey hain ke maine Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko paya ke unhoney rangeen kapdey pehney hain aur apni manzil ko bhi unhoney mua'ttar (khushbudaar) kar rakha hai. (Hazrat Ali ko tajjub hua) to wo bolin : aap hairaan kyon hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney as-haab ko hukm diya hai aur wo halal ho gaey hain. wo kehtey hain ke maine Fatima se kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) waley ehram ki niyat kar rakhi hai. kehtey hain, chunanche main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney puchha : ''tum ne (niyat) kaisey ki hai?'' maine kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehram wali niyat ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''main apni qurbani sath laya hun aur Quran ki niyat ki hai.'' wo bayan kartey hain ke phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke sarsath (67) ya chhiyasath (66) oont nahar (qurbaan) karo aur tentis ya chauntees oont apney liye ley lo aur her qurbani mein se gosht ka eik eik tukda merey liye lao.''"
1798,Abu-Waeil bayan kartey hain ke Janab Sabi bin Maabad ne kaha ke maine hajj aur Umerey dono ka ikhattey hi talbiya kaha hai to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tumhen apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tareeqey ki hidayat mili hai.
1799,"Abu-Waeil kehtey hain ke Janab Sabi bin Maabad ne kaha ke main eik badwi nasrani aadmi tha, musalman ho gaya. phir main apney qabiley ke eik aadmi ke paas aaya jis ka naam Hadeem bin Surmula tha. maine us se kaha : arey miyan ! main jihad ka laalchi hun magar hajj aur Umra bhi mujh par lazim ho chukey hain to agar main un dono (hajj aur umrey) ko jama kar lun to kaisa rahega? usney kaha : un dono ko jama kar lo aur jo muyassar ho qurbani kar lo. chunanche maine un dono ki niyat se talbiya kaha (aur ehram baandha) jab main uzaib ke maqam par pahuncha to mujhey Salman bin Rabeea aur Zaid bin Suhaan miley aur main hajj aur Umerey dono ka talbiya pukar raha tha. to un mein se eik ne doosrey se kaha : ye apney oont se ziyada samajh daar nahin hai ! (bewqoof hai ke hajj aur Umerey ka ikhattey talbiya pukar raha hai) Subai bayan kartey hain ke unki is baat se goya mujh par pahad toot pada yahan tak ke main umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur un se kaha : aey Ameerul-momineen ! main eik badwi nasrani aadmi tha aur musalman ho gaya hun, jihad par janey ka laalchi hun magar maine dekha ke hajj aur Umra bhi mujh par wajib ho chuka hai to main apni qaum ke eik aadmi ke paas aaya, usney mujhey kaha ke hajj aur Umerey ko ikhatta kar lo aur jo muyassar ho qurbani kar lo. chunanche maine un dono ka ikhattey talbiya pukara hai. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey farmaya : tumhen tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tareeqey ki hidayat mili hai."
1800,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se bayan kiya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna jabkey aap wadi aqeeq mein they, aap farma rahey they : ''aaj raat merey paas merey Shan Wale Rab ki taraf se eik aaney wala aaya aur usney kaha hai : us Mubarak wadi mein Namaz padho aur usney kaha ke Umra hajj mein dakhil hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko Waleed bin Muslim aur umr bin Abdul-Waahid ne Auzaai se bayan kiya to sirf isi qadr kaha : (وقل عمرة في حجة) (keh do ke Umra hajj mein dakhil hai. aur lafz (قال) ki bajaey (وقل) kaha.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke aisey hi Ali bin Mubarak ne Yahya bin Abi Kaseer se (hukm ke andaaz mein) (وقل عمرة في حجة) bayan kiya hai."
1801,"Janab Rabeea bin Sabra apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey yahan tak ke jab ham maqame-asfaan mein they to Suraqa bin Malik Mudliji (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamein khoob wazeh farma diijiye aur hamein aisi qaum samajhiye jo goya aaj hi paida huey ho. aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne tumharey is hajj mein Umerey ko dakhil kar diya hai, so jab tum Makka pahuncho to jisney Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee kar li , isliye wo halal ho gaya siwaey iske ke uskey sath qurbani ho.''"
1802,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen bataya ke maine Marwa par eik teer ke phal se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal kaatey they. ... . ya . ... . maine dekha ke Marwa par teer ke phal se aap ke baal kaatey gaey . abu-Bakar bin khallad ne ( أخبره (ka lafz istimal nahin kya ( balke yun kaha : ( (إن معاوية بن ابی سفیان قال)
1803,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : kya tumhen maloom nahin ke maine Marwa par eik badwi ke teer (ke phal) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal kaatey they. Hasan bin Ali ki riwayat mein izafa hai : ''hajj ke moqe par.''
1804,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umerey ka talbiya pukara aur aap ke as-haab ne hajj ka.
1805,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatil-wadaa mein Umerey ko hajj ke sath mila kar tamatto kya. ( tamatto ka lughwi maani , istifaada hai. ( aapney zal-Hulaifa se qurbani li aur apney sath ley gaey . ibtida (shuruat) mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umerey ka talbiya kaha aur phir hajj ka . aur logon ne bhi aap ke sath Umerey ko hajj ke sath mila kar tamatto kya. logon mein se kuch to wo they jo qurbaaniyan apney sath ley gaey aur kuch wo they jo na ley gaey. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka pahunchey to logon se farmaya : ''tum mein se jo shakhs qurbani laya hai uskey liye haram honey wali koi cheez halal nahin yahan tak ke apna hajj mukammal kar ley . lekin jo qurbani nahin laya hai to usey chahiye ke Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee karey aur uskey baad apney baal katarwa kar halal ho jaey. phir uskey baad hajj ka ehram baandhey aur qurbani dey . aur jo qurbani ki istataat na paey to wo hajj ke dono mein teen din rozey rakhey aur mazeed saat din apney ehle mein wapis lot kar rakhey .'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Makka pahunchney par tawaf kya aur sab se pehley rukn ( Hajre-Aswad ( ko bosa diya. phir tawaf ke saat chakkaron mein se ( pehley ( teen chakkaron mein aahista aahista dodey aur baqi chaar mein (aam raftaar sey) chaley. tawaf ke baad aapney maqame-Ibrahim ke paas do rakatein padhin, phir salam phera . phir aap Safa ki taraf aaye aur Safa Marwa par saat chakkar lagaey . phir aap par haram honey wali chizon mein se koi bhi chiz halal na hui . (isi tarah ehram hi mein rahey ( yahan tak ke apna hajj mukammal kya. daswin taareekh ko qurbani ki aur tawafe-ifaza kya, phir aap ke liye tamam chizen halal ho gaeen jo ehram ki halat mein haraam thin . aur deegar logon ne bhi jo qurbaaniyan apney sath laye they usi tarah kya jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kya."
1806,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! logon ka kya haal hai ke halal ho gaey hain jabkey aap apney Umerey se halal nahin huey? aapney farmaya : ''maine apney sar ke baal chupka rakhey hain aur apni qurbani ko qalada pehnaya hua hai, so main us waqt tak halal nahin ho sakta jab tak ke qurbani nahar na kar lun .''"
1807,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) us shakhs ke baarey mein kaha kartey they jo hajj ki niyat karey phir usey tod dey, Umra bana dey, ye sirf un logon ke liye tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein they."
1808,Haris bin Bilal apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya hajj ko fasakh kar dena hamarey liye khas hai ya hamarey baad walon ke liye bhi hai? aapney farmaya : '' balke ye tumharey hi liye khas hai.''
1809,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke) unke bhai ( Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sawari par unke peechey bethey huey they ke qabeela Khasham ki eik aurat aap se kuch poochhney ko aai to fazal usey dekhney lagey aur wo unhen dekhney lagi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Fazal ka chehra dusri taraf pher diya. us aurat ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ka fariza hajj uskey bandon mein, merey walid ko us haalat mein pahuncha hai ke wo sawari par tikney ki sakat bhi nahin rakhtey, to kya main unki taraf se hajj karun ? aapney farmaya : '' haan '' aur ye Hajjatil-wadaa ka waqia hai."
1810,bano Aamir ke eik shakhs abu-Rizeen ne bayan kya ke unhoney puchha tha ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey walid bahut boodhey hain aur hajj Umerey ki taqat nahin rakhtey aur na sawari par Sawar ho saktey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney baap ki taraf se hajj karo aur Umra ( bhi .'' (
1811,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko suna ke wo keh raha tha (لبيك an شبرمة) ''main shabarma ki taraf se hazir hun.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : '' shabarma kon hai? ''usney kaha ke mera bhai hai ya qaribi hai. aapney puchha : ''kya tum ne apni taraf se hajj kar liya hai? '' usney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : '' ( pehley ( apni taraf se hajj karo, phir shabarma ki taraf se karna.''"
1812,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke talbiya ke alfaz is tarah they. ... . ( لبَّيْكَ اللَّهُمَّ لَبَّيْكَ , لَبَّيْكَ ! لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ ! إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ وَالنِّعْمَةَ لَكَ وَالْمُلْكَ , لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ ) ''hazir hun mein aey Allah ! hazir hun. hazir hun, tera koi shareek nahin. main hazir hun. be-shak tamam taarifen aur nematein teri hain aur mulk bhi tera hi hai, tera koi shareek nahin .'' Naafe ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) apney talbiya mein izafa kartey huey yun kaha kartey they : ( لَبَّيْكَ ! لَبَّيْكَ ! لَبَّيْكَ ! وَسَعْدَيْكَ وَالْخَيْرُ بِيَدَيْكَ وَالرَّغْبَاءُ إِلَيْكَ وَالْعَمَلُ ) ''main hazir hun, main hazir hun, main hazir hun aur bahut saadat mand hun. khair aur bhalai sab terey haathon mein hai. hamari sab raghbatein aur sawal teri taraf hain aur amal bhi terey hi liye hain.''"
1813,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram baandha aur talbiya padha . aur Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki riwayat ki manind talbiya ke alfaz bayan kiye. kaha ke log ( ذا المعارج ! (aur is tarah ke alfaz ziyada kartey they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen suntey aur unhen kuch na kehtey they. ( ذا المعارج ! ( yani aey Allah bulandiyon waley aur inaamat ke malik!)
1814,Janab khallad bin Saaib Ansari apney walid se naqal kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas Jibrael Alehissalam aaye aur mujhey hukm diya ke main apney Sahaba aur doosrey sath walon ko hukm dun ke talbiya kehney main apni aawazen oonchi rakhen .'' raawi kehta hai ke aap ke alfaz ( بالإهلال ( they ya ( بالتلبية ( ) maani eik hi hain ( .
1815,Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( daswin zul-hijja ko) jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarney tak talbiya kehtey rahey .
1816,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, kehtey hain ke ham (nawin taareekh ko) subh ke waqt Mina se Arafat ki taraf rawana huey to kuch log ham mein se talbiya pukar rahey they aur kuch takbir ."
1817,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' Umra kerney wala Hajre-Aswad ko haath laganey (ya bosa denay) tak talbiya kehta rahey. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Abdul-Malik bin abi Suleman aur Hammam ne Ata se unhoney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se moquf riwayat kya hai.
1818,"Dukhtar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein hajj ke liye nikley. jab ham maqame-araj par pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne padaaw kiya aur ham bhi utar padey. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath baithin aur main apney walid (Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ke paas baithi. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samane-safar ka janwer eik hi tha jo Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik ghulam ki tahweel (sipurdigi) mein tha. Hazrat abu-Bakar baithey uska intizar kar rahey they ke wo aa jaey. chunanche jab wo aaya to wo oont uskey sath nahin tha. unhoney puchha : wo tera oont kahan hai? usney kaha : wo aaj raat gum ho gaya hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : sirf eik oont aur wo bhi to ne gum kar diya? aur phir usey maarney lagey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskuraatey rahey aur farmaney lagey : ''dekho is mahram ko , kya kar raha hai?'' ibne-Abi Rizma ke alfaz hain (فما يزيد رسول الله . . ۔) yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se ziyada na kaha ke ''dekho is mahram ko , kya kar raha hai !'' aur muskuraatey rahey ."
1819,Janab Safwan apney walid Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap maqame-ja'araana mein they aur us aadmi par khalooq khushbu ka asar tha ( jo ke Zaafran waghaira se bani hoti hai) ya kaha zard rang ki khushbu thi. aur wo jubba pehney huey tha. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey kya irshad farmatey hain ke main apney Umerey mein kaisey karun? tu Allah tabarak w taala ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par wahi nazil farmae. jab aap se ye keyfiyat door hui to puchha : ''wo Umerey ke mutalliq poochhney wala kahan hai?'' aapney us se farmaya : ''khalooq khushbu dho dalo.'' ya farmaya : ''zard rang dho dalo jubba utaar do aur apney Umerey mein wohi kuchh karo jo tum apney hajj mein kartey ho.''
1820,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ye qissa riwayat kartey huey kehtey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''apna jubba utaar do.'' chunanche usney usey apney sar ki taraf se utaar diya. aur hadees bayan ki."
1821,Hazrat Yaala ibn Muniyaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye khabar riwayat ki. is mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke isey utaar do (jubba ko) aur ghusl karo do baar ya teen baar . aur hadees bayan ki.
1822,"Janab Safwan apney walid Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kartey hain ke ja'araana ke maqam par eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, usney Umerey ka ehram baandha hua tha, jubba pehney huey tha aur uski dadhi aur sar mein zard rang ki khushbu lagi hui thi. aur mazkura baala hadees bayan ki."
1823,"Janab Salim apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha ke mahram kon se kapdey na pehney? aapney farmaya : ''qamis , topi daar karta , shalwaar , pagdi ya aisa kapda jis ko waras ya Zaafran laga ho na pehney aur mozey bhi na pehney , siwaey iske ke kisi ke paas jootey na hon. jiskey paas jootey na hon wo mozey pehan ley magar unhen kaat ley yahan tak ke takhnon se nichey ho jaeyn.''"
1824,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kartey hain."
1825,"Janab Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya hai aur mazeed kaha hai : ''ehram wali aurat naqaab pehney na dastaane pehney. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye hadees Hatim bin Ismael aur Yahya bin Ayub ne Musa bin Aqba sey, unhoney Naafe se usi tarah riwayat ki hai jaisey ke Leis ne riwayat ki hai. magar isko Musa bin Tariq ne Musa bin Aqba se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) par mauqufan riwayat kiya hai. aur aisey hi Ubaidullah bin umr , Malik aur Ayub ne bhi mauqufan riwayat kiya hai jabkey Ibrahim bin Saeed Madni ne Naafe sey, unhoney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya ke ''ehram wali, naqaab lagaey na dastaane pehney. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Ibrahim bin Saeed Madni ehale-Madina mein se sirf eik shaikh (aalim) hain koi ziyada sahibe-hadees nahin hain. (unki riwayat aagey aa rahi hai : 1826)."
1826,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''ehram wali aurat na naqaab lagaey aur na dastaane pehney.''
1827,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna ke aapney aurton ko ehram mein dastaane pehanney aur naqaab laganey se mana farmaya hai. aur aisey libas se bhi jisey waras (eik rang daar buti) aur Zaafran lagi ho. unke alawa jo libas aur rang chahey pehan ley (yani) Asfar (zard) rang ho ya resham, ya zewar ya shalwaar ya qamis ya moza. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Abda bin Sulaiman aur Muhammad bin Salma , Muhammad bin Is'haq se aur wo Naafe se riwayat kartey hain magar sirf us hissey tak (yani ( (وما مس الورس والزعفران من الثياب) baad wala hissey ye dono riwayat nahin kartey."
1828,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhen sardi lagi to unhoney kaha : aey Naafe ! mujh par koi kapda dal do. chunanche main (Naafe)  ne un par eik barans (eik qamis jis ka eik hissey bataur topi istimal hota hai) dal di. to wo boley : mujh par ye dal raha hai halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mahram ko iskey pehanney se mana farmaya hai.
1829,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kehtey huey suna : ''jisey tehband na miley wo shalwaar pehan ley aur jiskey paas jootey na hon wo mozey pehan ley. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye ehale-Makka ki riwayat hai aur iska mahwar ehale-Basra mein se Jabir bin Zaid (Rahimahullah) hain. is riwayat mein infiraadiyat ye hai ke is mein ''saraaweel'' (shalwaar) ka zikr hai aur mozon ke baarey mein kaatney ki hidayat nahin hai."
1830,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath main Makka ko jaten to ehram ke waqt apni peshaniyon par khushbudar murakkab khushbu ka zamaad (lep) kar liya karti thin. jab paseena aata to wo hamarey chehron par beh aata tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey dekhtey to us se mana na farmatey they."
1831,Janab Salim bin Abdullah apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke mutalliq bayan kartey hain ke wo ehram wali aurat ko kaha kartey they ke apney mozey kaat ley. phir (unki zauja)(biwi)  Safiya binte-abi Ubaid ne unhen bayan kiya ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton ko mozey pehanney ki rukhsat di hai. to wo apni baat se ruk gaey.
1832,Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hudebiya walon se suleh ki thi to is baat par suleh ki thi ke ye log (musalman) Makka mein is haalat mein dakhil hongey ke unke hathiyar unke miyaanon mein hongey. (ghaaliban) Shoba ne Abu-Is'haq se puchha ke ''(جلبان السلاح)'' kya hota hai? unhoney kaha chamdey ka wo thailaa jis mein hathiyar rakha jata hai.
1833,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ehram se hoti thin aur qafiley waley hamarey samney se guzartey to ham apney pardey ki chadar ko sar se chehrey par latka letin. jab wo guzar jatey to chehra khol leti thin.
1834,Hazrat Umme-Husain (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein Hijjatul-wadaa kiya. chunanche maine Hazrat Usama aur Bilal (Raziallahu anha) ko dekha ke un mein se eik Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni ki mahaar (nakel) pakdey huey tha aur doosra aap ko garmi se bachaney ke liye aap par kapda buland kiye huey tha (aur unki ye khidmat isi tarah rahi) yahan tak ke aapney Jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maar lin.
1835,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram ki haalat mein seengi lagwaai thi.
1836,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram ki haalat mein apney sar main eik bimari ki bina par seengi lagwaai.
1837,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bahaalate-ehram apney paon ki pusht par , eik takleef ki wajeh se seengi lagwaai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Imam Ahmed se suna, wo kehtey they ke ibne-Abi Aruba ne is riwayat ko Qatada se mursal bayan kiya. (yani Janab Anas ka wastey zikr nahin kiya.)"
1838,Janab Nabih bin Wahab (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke umr bin Ubaidullah bin Maamer ki aankhen kharab ho gaeen to unhoney Janab Aban bin Usman se puchha ke kya kiya jaey? Sufiyan ne bataya ke ye un dino ameere-hajj they. unhoney jawab diya ke elwey ka lep kar ley. be-shak maine Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha wo ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey they.
1839,"Usman bin Abi Sheba ne usey hamein Ismail bin Ibrahim sey, unhoney Naafe sey, unhoney Nabih bin Wahab se mazkura baala riwayat bayan ki."
1840,"Abdullah bin Hunain se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas aur Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu Anhuma) abwaa maqam mein they ke un main eik masley mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke mahram apna sar dho sakta hai. miswar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mahram apna sar nahin dho sakta. chunanche ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne usko ( Abdullah bin Hunain ko) Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bhej diya to usney unko paya ke wo kunwen ki charkhi ki do lakdiyon ke paas baithey ghusl kar rahey they aur eik kapdey se parda kiye huey they. kehtey hain ke maine unko salam kiya to unhoney puchha : kon ho? maine kaha : main Abdullah bin Hunain hun. mujhey Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bheja hai ke aap se daryaft karun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalate-ehram mein apna sar kaisey dhoya kartey they? to unhoney (Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne) apna haath (pardey waley) kapdey par rakh kar usey kuchh neecha kiya yahan tak ke mujhey unka sar nazar aaney laga. phir unhoney eik shakhs se jo un par pani dal raha tha, kaha ke pani dalo. chunanche usney unke sar par pani dala to Hazrat Abu-Ayub ne apney sar ko dono haathon se harkat di aur apney haathon ko aagey peechhey kiya : phir kaha : maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha tha ke aap isi tarah kartey they."
1841,"Janab umr bin Ubaidullah ne Janab Aban bin Usman bin Affan se kehla bheja jabkey Aban un dino ameere-hajj they aur ye dono ehram ki haalat mein they ke mera program hai ke Talha bin umr ka nikah Sheba bin Jubair ki saahibzaadi se kar dun. aur main chahta hun ke aap bhi is mein tashrif laeyn. to Janab Aban ne is se inkar kar diya aur kaha : maine apney walid Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai, wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''mohrim apna nikah karey na kisi doosrey ka.''"
1842,"Janab Aban bin Usman, Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : aur uper wali hadees ke misl zikr kya. aur mazeed kaha : '' aur na shaadi ka pegham dey .''"
1843,"Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke bhatijey Yazid bin Asamm Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se maqam Sarf mein nikah kya tha aur ham dono halal they."
1844,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Memuna se nikah kya jabkey aap haalate-ehram mein they.
1845,Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko Hazrat Memuna ke nikah ke mamley mein weham hua hai ke wo ehram mein they.
1846,"Janab Salim apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya gaya ke mehram kon se janwer qatl kar sakta hai? aapney farmaya : '' paanch janweron ke qatl mein koi gunah nahin hai. Haram mein maarey ya us se bahir hal mein (aur haalate-ehram mein maarey ya halal hotey huye,) yani bichhu, kawwa, chuha, cheel aur kaatney wala kutta.''"
1847,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' paanch qism ke janweron ko Haram mein qatl karna halal hai, yani saanp , bichhu, cheel, chuha aur kaatney wala kutta .''"
1848,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya mahram kon se janwer qatl kar sakta hai? aapney farmaya : '' saanp , bichhu, chuha, kowey ko pathar maarey qatl na karey, kaatney wala kutta , cheel aur her hamla aawar darinda.''"
1849,"Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Haris apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Janab Haris Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki janib se taaif ke governer they. unhoney Hazrat Usman ke liye khaney ka ehtimam kya aur us mein chakoron, jangli chidiyon aur neel gaey ka gosht tayyar karwaya. aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi bulwa bheja . qaasid jab unke paas pahuncha to wo apney oonton ke liye pattey jhaad rahey they. chunanche wo apney haath ( patton ke gird ghubar sey) jhaadtey huey tashrif laye . sahab ziyaafat ne un se kaha : khaaiye ! to unhoney jawab diya : ye khana aisey logon ko dey den jo ehram mein na hon, ham to ehram mein hain. tab unhon ( Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main qasam de-kar kehta hun ke qabeela Ashja mein se kon yahan hai, kya tum jantey ho ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haalate-ehram mein neel-gaey ka gosht hadiya kya tha, to aapney uskey khaney se inkar kar diya tha? un logon ne kaha : haan ( ye baat haq aur sach hai. ("
1850,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai unhoney kaha : aey Zaid bin Arqam ! kya tumhen maloom hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik shikar ka uzu hadiya diya gaya tha to aapney usey qubul nahin kya tha aur farmaya tha : '' ham ehram mein hain ?'' Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : haan !
1851,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna kehtey they : '' khushki ka shikar tumharey liye halal hai b-sharte-ke tum ne usko shikar na kya ho ya tumharey liye shikar na kya gaya ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se do hadisein eik-doosri ke bar-khilaf milen to wo hadees li jaey jis par aap ke Sahaba ne amal kya ho.
1852,Hazrat abu-Qatada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they yahan tak ke Makka ke raastey main eik jagah wo apney sathiyon ke sath peechey reh gaey jo ke ehram mein they jabke ye baghair ehram ke they. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik neel-gaaey ko dekha to apney ghodey par Sawar ho gaey aur sathiyon se kaha : mujhey mera kudra pakda do. unhoney kudra deney se inkar kar diya. phir bhala manga to unhoney us (ke deney) se bhi inkar kar diya. aakhir khud hi uthaya aur us neel-gaaey ke peechey bhag gaey aur usey maar laye . to kuch as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska gosht khaya aur kuch ne inkar kar diya. phir jab ye hazraat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ja miley to aap se uskey baarey mein daryaft kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to rizq hai jo Allah ne tumhen khilaya hai.''
1853,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tiddi samandar ke shikar (ki qism) mein se hai.''"
1854,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamen eik tiddi dal mil gaya to hamara eik aadmi jo ehram mein tha, unko apney kodey se maarney laga, usey kaha gaya ke ye kaam durust nahin hai aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''ye to samandar ke shikar mein se hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (us hadees ka raawi ( abu-Mehzam zaeef hai aur ye dono hadisein weham hain."
1855,Janab Kab (ahbar (Rahimahullah)) se manqul hai ke tiddi samandar ke shikar mein se hai.
1856,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hudebiya ke dino mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas se guzrey aur farmaya : '' tumharey sar ki juon ne tumhen eza (takleef) dey rakhi hai? '' unhoney kaha : haan ! to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sar munda lo aur phir eik bakri qurban kar do ya teen din rozey rakho ya teen saa khajoor chhe miskeenon mein taqseem kar do .''
1857,"Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' chaho to qurbani dey do , chaho to teen din rozey rakh lo aur agar chaho to teen saa khajoor chhe miskeenon ko khila do .''"
1858,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Hudebiya ke dino mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas se guzrey aur qissa bayan kya. aapney puchha : ''kya tumharey paas khoon ( fidye ka janwer ( hai? '' unhoney kaha ! nahin. aapney farmaya : '' to teen din rozey rakho ya teen saa khajoor chhe miskeenon mein sadqa kar do . her do miskeenon ko eik saa do .''
1859,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. aur unki haalat ye thi ke sar mein aziyat thi (yani juein pad gaee thin ( to unhoney apna sar mundwa liya tha. pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko hukm diya tha ke eik gaey ki qurbani karen.
1860,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey sar mein juein pad gaeen. jabkey main Hudebiya ke saal (us safar mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha. aur) sar ki aziyat itni shadeed thi ke) mujhey apni nazar ka andesha lag gaya tha. pas Allah azz-w-jall ne merey baarey mein ye aayat utari : ( فَمَنْ كَانَ مِنْكُمْ مَرِيضًا أَوْ بِهِ أَذًى مِنْ رَأْسِهِ . ... .) pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulwaya aur farmaya : '' apna sar munda do . teen rozey rakho ya chhe miskeenon ko eik tokra kishmish ka khila do ya eik bakri qurbani kar do .'' chunanche maine apna sar mundwaya aur phir qurbani kar di.
1861,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) se is qissey mein marwi (bayan) hai ke (aapney farmaya :) '' in (teen kamon) mein se jo bhi karogey tum se kifaayat kerega.''
1862,"Hazrat Hajjaj bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski haddi toot jaey ya langda ho jaey to wo halal ho gaya. (yani uskey liye halal ho jana jayez hai) aur aainda ke liye us par hajj hai. Janab Ikrima kehtey hain : maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Anhuma) se is baarey mein poochha, un dono ne (Hajjaj ki riwayat ki) tasdeeq ki."
1863,Hazrat Hajjaj bin Amr Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jiski haddi toot jaey ya wo langda ho jaey ya bimar pad jaey.'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya.  (Imam Abu-Dawud ke shekh) Janab Salma bin shabeeb ne apni sanad mein ''أنبأنا '' (yani ham ko khabar di (ka kalma istimal kya. (us tarah unhoney apney Shekh se samaa ki tasreeh kar di. (
1864,Amr bin Memun kehtey hain ke maine Abu-Hazir Himyari ko suna wo merey walid Memun bin Mehraan se bayan kar rahey they ke jis saal ahle-Sham ne Makka mein ibne-Zubair ka muhaasra (gheraw) kya tha main (Abu-Hazir Himyari) Umerey ki gharz se rawana hua. merey sath qom ke kuch afrad ne apni qurbaniyan bhi bheji thin. jab ham ahle-Sham ke paas pahunchey to unhoney hamen Haram mein dakhil honey se rok diya. chunanche maine qurbani usi jagah nahar kar di aur phir halal ho gaya aur wapis lot aaya. phir jab aglaa saal aaya aur main apney Umerey ki qaza ke liye chala to Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan aaya aur un se puchha to unhoney kaha : apni qurbani ka badal bhi do. be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umra qaza mein apney Sahaba se farmaya tha ke Hudebiya ke saal unhoney jo qurbaaniyan ki thin unke iwaz qurbaaniyan bhi karen.
1865,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo jab bhi Makka aatey to wadiye-zi tuwa mein raat guzaartey yahan tak ke subh ho jati aur ghusl kartey. phir din chadhey Makka mein dakhil hotey. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mutalliq bayan kartey ke aapney aisey hi kya tha.
1866,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein baalai (upri) janib ki ghaati se tashrif laya kartey they. Musaddad aur ibne-Hanbal ne Yahya se naqal kartey huey kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Batha ki ghaati se Kada ki janib se Makka mein dakhil hotey they aur zereen janib ki ghaati se wapis jatey they. barmaki ( Abdullah bin Jaafar ( ne mazeed kaha ke Makka ki do ghaatiyaan murad hain. aur Musaddad ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai.
1867,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Madina munawwara sey) nikaltey huey shajra wali raah ikhtiyar farmatey. (yani zal-Hulaifa wali, jahan us zamaney main eik darkht bhi tha. (aur wapsi mein Muarras wali janib se dakhil hotey. (yani Madina mein)"
1868,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh ke saal Makka mein uski baalai (upri) janib kadaa ki taraf se dakhil huey they. aur Umra mein Kada ki taraf (nichey ki janib) se aaye they. aur Janab Urwa dono raahon se aatey they. ( kabhi us se aur kabhi us sey) aur ye ( Urwa ( aksar oqaat Kada ki taraf (nichey ki taraf ( se dakhil hotey they. aur ye janib unki manzil ke ziyada qarib thi.
1869,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka mein dakhil hotey to uski baalai janib se tashrif latey. (usi raastey main Makka ka maroof qabristaan hai aur us taraf se aaney mein aap ko aasani thi aur wapsi ke liye ( nichey ki taraf se nikaltey they. (aur yehi wo raah hai jismein aajkal maqam ''jarwal'' aata hai. (
1870,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha gaya ke aadmi Baitullah ko dekh kar haath uthaey (ya nahin?) unhoney kaha : maine yahudiyon ke ilawa kisi ko aisey kartey huey nahin dekha. (wo log baitul-Maqdis ko dekh kar haath uthatey hain) aur ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein hajj kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey nahin kya tha.
1871,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka mein dakhil huey to Baitullah ka tawaf kya aur maqame-Ibrahim ke peechey do rakatein padhin, yani Fateh Makka waley din."
1872,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, pas Makka mein dakhil huye, phir Hajre-Aswad ki taraf tashrif laye, usey bosa diya. phir Baitullah ka tawaf kya, phir Safa ki janib aaye aur uskey ooper chadh gaey jahan se Baitullah aap ko nazar aa raha tha, phir aapney apney dono haath utha liye aur Allah ka zikr kartey rahey jis qadr ke Allah ne chaha aur dua kartey rahey . aur ansaar aap ke sath they. hadees ke raawi Hashim ne kaha : dua farmaai, Allah ki hamd ki aur jo chaha dua ki ."
1873,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo Hajre-Aswad ke paas aaye aur usko bosa diya, phir kaha : bila-shuba main janta hun ke to mehaz eik pathar hi hai, na nafa dey sakta hai na nuqsan agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko na dekha hota ke unhoney tujhey bosa diya tha to main tujhey bosa na deta."
1874,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap Baitullah ke sirf do Yamani arkaan hi ko haath lagatey they.
1875,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka ye bayan bataya gaya ke Hajar (yani hateem) ka kuch hissey Baitullah mein se hai, to unhoney kaha : qasam Allah ki ! mera khayal hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne agar ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hai to main samajhta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi un ( Shami ( arkaan ka istilaam ( mas karna ( sirf isi liye tark farmaya tha ke ye Baitullah ki asal buniyaadon par nahin hain. aur log bhi hajr ( hateem (ke bahir se usi bina par tawaf kartey hain."
1876,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tawaf ke kisi chakkar mein bhi rukn Yamani aur Hajre-Aswad ka istilaam (yani usey mas karna ( na chhodtey they. ( Naafe ne ( kaha : aur Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bhi aisey hi kya kartey they.
1877,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatil-wadaa mein oont par Sawar ho kar tawaf kya. aap apney asa se rukn ( Hajre-Aswad ( ko mas kartey they.
1878,Safiya bint Shaiba (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Fateh Makka ke saal jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Makka mein itminan hasil ho gaya to aapney apney oont par) Sawar ho kar) tawaf kya. kehti hain ke main aap ko dekh rahi thi ke aap apney asa se rukn ( Hajre-Aswad (ka istilaam farmatey they.
1879,Hazrat abu-Tufail ( Aamir bin Waasila ( (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap apni sawari par Sawar Baitullah ka tawaf kar rahey they. apney asa se rukn ( Hajre-Aswad (ka istilaam kartey they aur phir usey bosa detey they. Muhammad bin Raafe ne mazeed kaha : phir aap Safa Marwa ki taraf tashrif ley gaey aur apni sawari par unke beech saat chakkar lagaey .
1880,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatil-wadaa main apni sawari par Sawar ho kar Baitullah ka tawaf kya aur Safa Marwa ki saee ki taake log aap ko dekh lein aur aap un se buland rahen aur wo aap se ( masayel ( daryaft kar saken kyonkey logon ne aap ko gher rakha tha.
1881,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mukarrma tashrif laye to aap ki tabiat naasaaz thi chunanche aapney apni sawari par) Sawar ho kar) tawaf kya. aap jab bhi Hajre-Aswad ke paas aatey to apney asa se usko mas kartey. pas jab aap apney tawaf se farigh ho gaey to aapney ( apni oontni ko) bitha diya aur do rakatein ada kin .
1882,ummul-momenin Hazrat umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai wo kehti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha ke meri tabiat kharab hai to aapney farmaya : '' sawari par beth kar logon ke peechey se tawaf kar lo.'' kehti hain : chunanche maine tawaf kya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us waqt Baitullah ke pehlu mein Namaz padha rahey they aur aap Sura Toor ki qirat farma rahey they.
1883,Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tawaf kya jabkey aap iztibaa kiye huey they aur chadar sabz (hare) rang ki thi.
1884,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ne maqam jaarana se (ehram baandh kar) Umra kya, to Baitullah mein unhoney ramal kya aur apni chaadaron ko apni baghlon ke nichey se baain kandhon par dal liya ."
1885,"Hazrat abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : aap ki qom ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Baitullah mein ramal kya tha aur ye ke ye sunnat hai. to wo boley ke unhoney sach kaha hai aur kuch ghalat . maine kaha : ( kya matlab ( kya sach kaha aur kya ghalat ? farmaya : ye to sach hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ramal kya tha, magar sunnat kehna ghalat hai. dar-haqeeqat Quraish ne Hudebiya ke zamaney mein kaha tha ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur unke as-haab ko chhod do yahan tak ke wo khud hi janweron ki maut mar jaeyngey .) jaisey oonton ki naakon mein keedey pad jatey hain aur phir wo halak ho jatey hain. ( phir jab unhoney aap se suleh kar li ke ye log agley saal ayen aur Makka mein teen din thehren , chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye to mushrekin ko Qaeeqaan ki janib ( se dekh rahey ( they. tab aapney apney as-haab se farmaya : ''Baitullah ke gird teen chakkar ramal karo.'' (yani kandhey hila hila kar aahista aahista dodo) aur ye koi sunnat nahin hai. maine kaha : aap ki qom ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safa aur Marwa ki saee oont par Sawar ho kar ki thi aur ye bhi sunnat hai. to wo boley : unhoney sach kaha hai aur kuch ghalat . maine kaha : kya sach hai aur kya ghalat ? farmaya : sach ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safa aur Marwa ki saee oont par ki thi magar ye sunnat ho, ghalat hai. ( darasal ( logon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se door na kya jata tha aur na hataya jata tha ( jabke wo aap par hujoom kiye huey they ( to aapney oont par Sawar ho kar saee ki taake wo aap ki baat sun saken , aap ko dekh saken aur unke haath aap tak na pahunch paeyn ."
1886,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein tashrif laye jabkey un logon ko Yasrib ( Madina ka sabiqa naam (ke bukhar ne kamzor kar diya tha to mushrekin ne kaha : tumharey paas eik aisi qom aa rahi hai jisey bukhar ne nidhal kar diya hai aur unhen us se badi aziyat pahunchi hai. Allah taala ne mushrekin ki is baat se jo unhoney kahi , apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bata diya. pas aapney unhen hukm diya ke teen chakkaron mein ramal keren aur rukn Yamani aur Hajre-Aswad ke darmiyan aam raftaar se chalen. so jab unhoney un logon ko ramal kartey dekha (ke badi phurti se tawaf kar rahey hain ( to kehney lagey : inhi logon ke baarey mein tum kehtey ho ke unko bukhar ne kamzor kar diya hai, ye to ham se ziyada taqatwar hain. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sahaba par shafqat farmatey huey tawaf ke sab chakkaron mein ramal ka hukm nahin diya tha."
1887,"Janab Aslam Adwi kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, farmatey they : aaj ye kandhey hila-hila kar daudna aur unka nanga karna kyon hai? (uski koi zarurat to nahin hai) halanke Allah taala ne Islam ko qawi aur mazboot bana diya hai aur kufr w kuffar ko yahan se nikal bahir kya hai. iskey bawajood ham ye amal nahin chhod saktey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein kya kartey they."
1888,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Baitullah ka tawaf, Safa Marwa ki saee aur jamaraat ko kankariyaan maarna, ye sab Allah ka zikr qaaim kerney ke liye hain.''"
1889,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne iztibaa kya. (apni chadar ko apni daain baghal ke nichey se nikal kar baain kandhey par dal liya .) phir ( Hajre-Aswad ka ( istilaam kya aur) الله أكبر ( kaha . phir teen chakkaron mein ramal kya. Sahaba jab rukn Yamani ke paas pahunchtey aur Quraish ki nazron se ojhal ho jatey to aam raftaar se chalney lagtey . phir jab unke samney aatey to aahista aahista dodney lagtey. Quraish kehney lagey : ye to goya hiran hain. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha : ( tab sey) ye sunnat hai.
1890,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ne Jaarana se Umra kya to unhoney Baitullah mein ramal kya aur) aakhiri ( chaar chakkaron mein aam raftaar se chaley .
1891,Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hajre-Aswad se Hajre-Aswad tak ramal kya. (yani purey chakkar mein) aur zikr kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye amal kya tha.
1892,Hazrat Abdullah bin Saaib (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap rukn Yamani aur Hajre-Aswad ke beech ye dua padh rahey they : ( رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً وَقِنَا عَذَابَ النَّارِ ( ''aey hamarey rab hamen duniya mein khair w bhalai inayat farma aur aakhirat mein bhi khair w bhalai dey aur hamen aag ke azab se mehfooz rakh .''
1893,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hajj aur Umra mein (Makka mein) aatey hi jo pehla tawaf (tawafe-qudoom) kartey to uskey teen chakkaron mein (aahista aahista) dodtey aur chaar mein aam raftaar se chaltey, phir do rakatein ada kartey."
1894,"Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' kisi ko mana mat karo jis waqt bhi koi is ghar ka tawaf karna chahey aur Namaz padhna chahey ( to padhney do .) din ho ya raat , chaahey koi waqt ho.'' Fazal-bin Yaqoob ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( khitab kartey huey farmaya ( ''aey bani Abd-Manaaf ! kisi ko mana mat karo.''"
1895,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba ne Safa aur Marwa ke beech eik hi baar saee ki thi. yani pehli baar tawaf qudoom ya tawafe-Umra ke sath .
1896,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke as-haabe-Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jo aap ke sath they unhoney jamara ko kankariyaan maarney ke baad hi tawaf kya tha.
1897,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya tha : '' tera Baitullah ka tawaf aur Safa Marwa ki saee , terey hajj aur Umerey ( dono ( ko kafi hai. Imam Shafai (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Sufiyan (bin Uena ( kabhi sanad yun bayan kartey : (عن عطاء an عائشة) aur kabhi yun kehtey : (عن عطاء أن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم قال لعائشة رضی اللہ عنہا)"
1898,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab Makka Fateh kya to maine kaha : main apney kapdey zarur pahnunga, mera ghar raastey hi par tha aur bil-zaroor dekhunga ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaisey kartey hain. chunanche main chala aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap aur aap ke Sahaba Kaaba ke andar se nikal chukey they aur darwazey se hateem tak Baitullah ke sath chimtey huey they. unhoney apney rukhsaar kaabey ke sath lagaey huey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke darmiyan mein they."
1899,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid (Shoaib bin Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Amr ( se bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tawaf kya. jab ham Kaaba ke peechey ki janib aaye to maine kaha : kya aap taawuz nahin kartey. unhoney kaha : ham Allah ki panah chahtey hain dozakh se. phir chaltey aaye yahan tak ke Hajre-Aswad ka istilaam kya aur Hajre-Aswad aur darwazey ke darmiyan ruk gaey phir apna seena aur chehra us par rakha, apni kalaaiyon aur haathon ko is tarah kya aur unhen khoob phelaya. (yani phela kar dikhaya.) phir kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is tarah kartey dekha hai."
1900,"Janab Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Saaib apney walid ( Abdullah bin Saaib ( se bayan kartey hain ke wo Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka haath pakad kar chaltey they (jabkey wo na-bina ho chukey they) aur unhen teesrey koney ke paas khada kar detey they jo ke Hajre-Aswad ke sath darwaza Kaaba ke paas hai, to Hazrat ibne-Abbas usey kehtey : ''kya khabar di gaee hai tumhen ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) yahan Namaz padha kartey they?'' to wo kehtey ke haan! phir wo khadey ho jatey aur Namaz padhtey ."
1901,"Janab Urwa (bin Zubair) kehtey hain ke maine ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha aur main un dino nau-umr tha : farmaiye Allah taala ke farman : ( إِنَّ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْوَةَ مِنْ شَعَائِرِ اللَّهِ ( se main ye samajhta hun ke agar koi unke darmiyan saee na karey to us par koi harj nahin ! Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : hergiz nahin, agar baat aisey hoti jaisey tum keh rahey ho to aayate-karima yun hoti : (فلا جناح عليه أن لا يطوف بهما) ''agar wo unki saee na karey to us par koi gunah nahin .'' darasal ye aayat ansaar ke baarey mein nazil hui thi. ye log manaat ( but (ke qasd se ehram baandha kartey they aur ye but maqame-qudaid ke bilmuqaabil nasb tha. aur phir ye log Safa Marwa ki saee mein harj samajhtey they. jab Islam aaya to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us baarey mein sawal kya to Allah azz-w-jall ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ( إِنَّ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْوَةَ مِنْ شَعَائِرِ اللَّهِ ("
1902,Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umra kya to Baitullah ka tawaf kya aur maqam ( Ibrahim (ke peechey do rakatein padhein . aur aap ke sath wo log they jinhon ne aap ko logon se bachaya hua tha. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaaba mein dakhil huey they? unhoney kaha : nahin.
1903,"Ismael bin abi Khalid kehtey hain, maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees suni . aur ye mazeed kaha : phir aap Safa Marwa ki taraf aaye aur unke darmiyan saat chakkar lagaey phir apna sar mundaya."
1904,"Kasir bin Jamhan se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se Safa aur Marwa ke darmiyan puchha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! main aap ko dekhta hun ke aap chal rahey hain jabkey log dod rahey hain. (kyon?) unhoney kaha : agar main chalun to bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko chaltey huey dekha hai. aur agar main dodun to maine aap ko dodtey huey dekha hai, aur main ( ab ( boodha ho gaya hun."
1905,"Hazrat Jaafar (Sadiq) bin Muhammad (bin Ali bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) apney walid ( Muhammad ( se bayan kartey hain ke ham Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke yahan gaey . jab ham aap ke paas pahunchey to unhoney sab logon se puchha ( jan-pehchan hasil ki), yahan tak ke meri baari aai to maine bataya ke main Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain hun. to unhoney apna haath merey sar ki taraf badhaya , phir mera ooper wala batan khola , phir nichey wala khola , phir apna haath meri chhaatiyon ke darmiyan rakha , aur main un dino jawan ladka tha. unhoney kaha : khush aamadeed , bhatijey ! apney hi ghar mein aaye ho ! (1) jo ji chahta hai poochh lo , chunanche maine un se puchha (2) jabkey wo na-bina ho chukey they. aur Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to wo apney usi chhotey se kapdey hi ko lapet kar khadey ho gaey . usey dohra karkey siya gaya tha. kapda is qadr chhota tha ke usey jab bhi kandhey par rakhtey, uskey kinarey gir padtey they, unhoney hamko Namaz padhaai halanke aap ki badi chadar aap ke pehlu mein khunti par lagi hui thi. (3) maine kaha : aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hajj ke baarey mein bayan farmaeyn, to unhoney apney haath se 9 ki gireh banai , phir kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) no saal tak rukey rahey aur hajj nahin kya, phir daswin saal logon mein aelan kya ke Allah ke Rasool hajj ke liye janey waley hain, chunanche Madina mein bahut ziyada log aa gaey. (4) her eik Allah ke Rasool ki iqtidaa aur aap ke amal ki perwi karna chahta tha. (5) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley to ham bhi aap ke sath they yahan tak ke maqam zal-Hulaifa par pahunch gaey. yahan Asma binte-Umais (zauja abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Muhammad bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ko janm diya. pas unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf pegham bheja ke main kaisey karun? aapney farmaya : ''ghusl karo, kapdey ka langot bandho aur ehram ki niyat kar lo.'' (6) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein Namaz padhi , phir ( apni oontni ( qaswaa ( 7 ( par Sawar ho gaey . yahan tak ke wo aap ko lekar Beda ( maidan (ke samney khadi ho gaee . Jabir bayan kartey hain : maine dekha nigah ki had tak aap ke samney, daeyn, baeyin aur peechey log hi log they. kuch Sawar aur kuch pedal. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan mein they, aap par Quran utar raha tha aur aap uska maani w mafhoom aur tariqa amal bhi khoob jantey they, chunanche jo aapney kya ham ne bhi wesay hi kya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kalima toheed pukara : ( لبَّيْكَ ! اللَّهُمَّ لَبَّيْكَ ! لَبَّيْكَ لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ لَبَّيْكَ ! إِنَّ الْحَمْدَ وَالنِّعْمَةَ لَكَ , وَالْمُلْكَ لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ ) ''hazir hun main aey Allah ! hazir hun, main hazir hun. tera koi sajhi nahin, main hazir hun, bila-shuba hamd teri hai, nematein teri hain aur mulk bhi tera hai, tera koi shareek nahin.'' aur logon ne bhi yehi talbiya pukara jo wo pukartey hain. aapney kisi ki tardid nahin farmaai . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney talbiya hi ka iltizaam farmaya. ( 8 ( Jabir kehtey hain ke hamari niyat sirf hajj ki thi, ham Umra nahin jantey they, yahan tak ke jab ham aap ke sath Baitullah mein pahunch gaey, Hajre-Aswad ka istilaam kya, ( 9 ( to teen chakkaron mein ramal kya. (aahista aahista dodey.) (10) aur chaar mein aam raftaar se chaley. phir aap Maqame-Ibrahim ki taraf aagey badh gaey aur ye aayat padhi واتخذُوا من مقامِ إبراهيمَ مُصلّٰى '' aur maqame-Ibrahim ko apni jaey-Namaz bana lo.'' aapney Maqame-Ibrahim ko apney aur Baitullah ke darmiyan kya (aur do rakatein padhin). (11) Jaafar (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke merey walid kaha kartey they : Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi se bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un do rakaaton mein) قل هو الله أحد (aur ( قل ya أيها الكافرون ( padhi . uskey baad aap Kaaba ki taraf lotey aur Hajre-Aswad ka bosa liya .) 12 ( phir baab Safa se Safa pahadi ki taraf tashrif ley gaey. pas jab Safa ke qarib pahunchey to ye aayat padhi : ( إِنَّ الصَّفَا وَالْمَرْوَةَ مِنْ شَعَائِرِ اللَّهِ ( '' Safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein se hain.'' (aur ye bhi kaha ( ) نَبدأُ بما بدأ اللهُ به ( '' ham us se ibtida (shuruat) kartey hain jis ka zikr Allah azz-w-jall ne pehley farmaya hai.'' chunanche aapney Safa se ibtida (shuruat) farmaai aur us par chadh gaey yahan tak ke Baitullah nazar aaney laga tu Allah ki takbir w toheed bayan farmaai aur kaha : ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , لَهُ الْمُلْكُ , وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ , يُحْيِي وَيُمِيتُ , وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ . لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ أَنْجَزَ وَعْدَهُ وَنَصَرَ عَبْدَهُ وَهَزَمَ الْأَحْزَابَ وَحْدَهُ ) ''eik Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud haqiqi nahin. wo akela hai uska koi sajhi nahin, saltanat uski hai, tareef ka haqdaar wohi hai. wohi zinda karta aur maarta hai, aur wo her chiz par puri qudrat rakhta hai. eik Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud haqeeqi nahin, wo akela hai. usney apna wada pura kar dikhaya. apney bandey ki madad farmaai aur tamam girohon ko us akeley hi ne paspa kar diya.'' phir uskey baad dua farmaey. aur is tarah teen baar (mazkura kalmaat) kahey aur (unke darmiyan mein) duayen kin. (13) phir aap Marwa ki janib utar aaye . jab aap ke qadam wadi ke darmiyan mein tik gaey to aapney uskey daman mein dod lagai. ( 14 ( yahan tak ke jab chadhai aai to chalney lagey yahan tak ke Marwa par pahunch gaey . aapney Marwa par bhi usi tarah kya jaisey ke Safa par kya tha. ( wohi kalmaat teen teen baar padhey aur unke darmiyan mein duayen kin .) jab aap ka aakhiri chakkar Marwa par khatam hua to farmaya : ''agar mujhey apney maamley ka pehley ilm hota jo baad mein hua, to main qurbani sath lekar na chalta aur main apney us tawaf ko Umra bana leta. pas tum logon mein se jis jiskey sath qurbani nahin hai wo halal ho jaey aur apney is tawaf ko Umra bana ley.'' ( 15 ( chunanche sab log halal ho gaey aur unhoney apney baal katarwa liye. ( 16 ( siwaye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur un logon ke jinkey sath qurbaniyan thin. Hazrat Suraqa (bin Malik) bin Jaasham (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! (hamara ye Umra) us saal ke liye hai ya hamesha ke liye? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungliyan eik dusri ke andar dakhil karkey ( ishara kartey huey ( farmaya : '' Umra hajj ke andar is tarah dakhil ho gaya hai.'' aapney do dafa farmaya : ''(is saal ke liye) nahin balke hamesha hamesh ke liye. nahin balke hamesha-hamesh ke liye.'' aur bayan kya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qurbaniyan lekar aaye. unhoney ( apni ehliya ( Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko dekha ke wo bhi un logon mein shamil hain jo halal ho chukey they. usney rangin kapdey pehan liye they aur surma lagaya tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne us par nagawari ka izhar kya. ( 17 ( puchha ke tumhen aisa kerney ka kis ne kaha hai? unhoney kaha : merey abba ne . Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jis zamaney mein Iraq mein they, bayan kya kartey they ke main Fatima ke us amal par jo usney kya tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf mansoob kya tha, naraz ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochhney ke liye gaya. maine aap ko bataya ke mujhey us ( Fatima (ka ye kaam nagawar guzra hai aur wo kehti hain ke merey abba ne mujhey ye hukm diya hai. aapney farmaya : '' wo sach kehti hai, sach kehti hai. ( 18 ( ) tum apney mutalliq batao ke) tum ne hajj ki niyat kartey waqt kya kaha tha ?'' kehney lagey ke maine kaha tha : aey Allah ! main wohi ehram baandh raha hun jis tarah ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baandha hai. aapney farmaya : ''merey sath to qurbani hai, chunanche tum bhi halal na ho.'' Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke wo qurbaniyan, jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Yamen se laye they aur jo khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina se laye they, unki kul tadaad eik so thi. chunanche sab log halal ho gaey aur apney baal katarwa liye, siwaye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur un logon ke jinkey sath qurbaniyan thin. phir jab (zul-hijja ki) aathwin tareekh aai (yomut-tarviya) ( 19 (aur log Mina ki taraf janey lagey to unhoney hajj ka ehram baandha . chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sawar ho gaey aur Mina ja kar Zohar , Asr , maghrib , Isha aur subh ki namazein padhin. ( 20 ( phir aap thodi der thehrey yahan tak ke Suraj nikal aaya . aapney apney liye baalon ke baney huey khemey ke mutalliq hukm diya aur wo namra mein laga diya gaya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaley ( 21 (aur Quraish ko yaqeen tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Muzdalfa mein mashare-haram ke paas hi ruk jaeyngey jaisey ke wo ( Quraish ( Islam se pehley jahiliyat mein kya kartey they. magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se aagey badh gaey yahan tak ke Arafat pahunchey .) 22 ( aapney dekha ke Namra mein khema laga hua hai. aap wahan utrey ( 23 ( yahan tak ke jab Suraj dhal gaya to aapney ( apni oontni ( qaswa ke mutalliq farmaya to usey tayyar kar diya gaya. aap us par Sawar huey yahan tak ke wadi ( Arna (ke daman mein aagey aur logon ko khutba diya. ( 24 ( aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba tumharey khoon aur tumharey maal tumharey darmiyan haram hain jaisey ke tumhara ye din , tumhara ye mahina aur tumhara ye shehar hurmat wala hai. khabrdar ! jahiliyat ke tamam umur (mamley) merey qadmon taley raundey ja rahey hain. jahiliyat ke) sab ( khoon khatam kiye jatey hain. aur sab se pehla , khoon jo main khatam karta hun wo hamara apna khoon hai.'' ibn Rabeea ka .) ye Imam Abu-Dawud ke ustaad ( Usman ne kaha : jabke ( ustaad ( Suleman ne kaha : '' Rabeea bin Haris bin abdul-Muttalib ka ( khoon khatam karta hun.'' ( unke baaz ne kaha : jo ke bani Saad mein doodh peeta bachcha tha aur bano huzail ne usey qatl kar diya tha.'' jahiliyat ke) tamam ( sood khatam kiye jatey hain. aur sab se pehla sood jo main khatam kar raha hun wo hamara apna sood . Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ka sood hai, ye sab khatam hai. ( 25 ( aurton ke baarey mein Allah se daro . tum ne Allah ki amanat se un par ikhtiyar hasil kya hai aur Allah ke kalme se unki ismaton ko halal jana hai. aur un aurton par bhi wajib hai ke tumharey huqooq ka lihaz rakhen .) aur wo ( ye ke tumharey bistaron par wo kisi ko na aaney den , jinka aana tumhen nagawar ho. ( tumharey gharon mein tumharey naa-pasandida afrad ko, mard hun ya aurten , na aaney den .) agar wo aisa keren to unhen maaro , magar zakhmi kerney wali maar na ho. aur tum par wajib hai ke unka naan w nafqa aur libas maroof andaz mein mohaiyya karo . bila-shuba main tum mein wo chiz chhodey ja raha hun ke agar tum usey mazboot se thaamey rahey, to gumrah na hogey (aur wo hai) Allah ki kitab .) 26 ( tum logon se merey baarey mein puchha jaeyga , to kya jawab dogey ?'' logon ne kaha : ham gawahi dengey ke bila-shuba aapney ( Allah ka pegham ( pahuncha diya. ( puri tarah ( ada kar diya aur khair khuwahi ( mein inteha ( kar di. aap apni shahadat ki ungli aasman ki taraf uthatey aur logon ki taraf jhukatey they aur kehtey they : ''aey Allah! gawah rehna. aey Allah! gawah rehna. aey Allah! gawah rehna.'' phir Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Azan kahi , phir iqaamat kahi to aapney Zohar ki Namaz padhaai. unhoney phir iqaamat kahi to aapney Asr ki Namaz padhaai . aur un ( dono namazon (ke darmiyan kuch nahin padha .) 27 ( (yani sunnat ya nafl ( phir aap qaswaa par Sawar ho gaey yahan tak ke maqam waquf par tashrif laye . apni oontni qaswaa ka pet patharon ki taraf kar diya. (yani wahin rukey rahey (aur Jabal المشاۃ ko) jo ke ret ka bada teela tha aur log usko pedal hi uboor kartey they ( apney samney kya, qibla rukh huey aur phir wahin rukey rahey yahan tak ke Suraj ghuroob ho gaya aur tikiya ke ghayeb ho janey ke baad kuch zardi bhi khatam ho gaee .) 28 ( phir aapney Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko apney peechey bitha liya aur chal diye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni oontni qaswa ki baag us sakhti se kheenchi hui thi ke uska sar paalaan ke sirey ko lag raha tha aur aap apney daain haath se ishara kartey huey farma rahey they : '' logo ! sukoon sey, logo ! sukoon se .'' ( 29 (aap jab kisi chadhai ke paas aatey to oontni ki baag qadrey dheeli kar detey taake (sahulat sey) chadh sakey .) 30 ( yahan tak ke aap Muzdalfa pahunch gaey aur maghrib aur Isha ki namazein eik Azan aur do iqaamaton ke sath jama karkey padhin. (31) Usman ne bayan kya : aapney unke darmiyan koi sunnat nafl nahin padhey. sab raawiyon ka muttafiqa bayan hai ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) let gaey yahan tak ke Fajr tulu ho gaee . jab subh numaya ho gaee to aapney Fajr ki Namaz padhaai. ( ustaad) Suleman ka bayan hai ke eik Azan aur eik iqaamat ke sath. (sab ka muttafiqa bayan hai) phir aap qaswa par Sawar huey yahan tak ke Mashare-Haram ke paas aa gaey, phir us par chadh gaey. Usman aur Suleman ka bayan hai ke aapney qibley ki taraf rukh kya. Allah ki hamd , takbir aur tahleel bayan ki . Usman ne izafa kya : aur toheed bayan ki . aur phir wahin rukey rahey yahan tak ke khoob safedi ho gaee. phir Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se chal diye , Suraj tulu honey se pehley hi. (32) aur Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko apney sath Sawar kar liya . aur wo qadrey ghungariyaley, khoob soorat baalon waley, gorey chattey, Husain w jameel jawan they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se rawana huey to aurten bhi apney kajawon mein bethi wahan se guzrin. Hazrat fazal (Raziallahu anhu) unhen dekhney lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey chehrey par haath rakh diya. fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna chehra dusri taraf pher liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi apna haath dusri taraf se pher diya phir fazal (Raziallahu anhu) apna chehra kisi aur taraf pher kar dekhney lagey. (33) yahan tak ke aap wadi mohsir mein pahunch gaey aur qadrey tez chaley. (34) phir aap darmiyan wali raah par chal padey jo tumhen jamara kubraa tak pahunchati hai yahan tak ke aap jamara ke paas aagey jo ke darkht ke paas hai. to aapney usko saat kankariyaan maaren jaisi ke ungliyon par rakh kar maari jati hain. her kankari ke sath aap ( الله اكبر ( kehtey they. aapney wadi ke daman ki taraf se kankariyan maaren. (35) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qurban-gaah ki taraf tashrif ley gaey aur apney haath se tiresath oontniyan nahar kin aur baqiya ke mutalliq Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya. aur unko apni qurbani mein shareek banaya. phir aapney her qurbani se eik eik tukda gosht leney ka hukm diya. usey deg mein dal kar pakaya gaya to aap dono ne us gosht mein se khaya aur shorba nosh farmaya. (37) Suleman ka bayan hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sawar huey aur Baitullah ki taraf chal diye aur Makka aa kar Zohar ki Namaz ada farmaey. (38) phir aap bani abdul-Muttalib ke paas aaye , wo log chaha zamzam par pani pila rahey they. aapney farmaya : ''aey bani abdul-Muttalib! pani nikalo. agar ye andesha na hota ke log tumharey us pani pilaney mein tum par ghalib aa jaeyngey to main bhi tumharey sath pani nikalta.'' (39) so unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik dol diya aur aapney us se pani piya. ( 40 ("
1906,"Janab Jaafar (Sadiq) (Rahimahullah) apney walid (Muhammad bin Ali (Rahimahullah)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arafat mein Zohar aur Asr ki namazein eik Azan aur do iqaamaton ke sath padhi thin, aur unke beech koi sunnatein ( nafl ( nahin padhey they. aur maghrib aur Isha ki namazein Muzdalfa main eik Azan aur do iqaamaton ke sath padhi thin aur unke beech koi sunnatein (nafl) nahin padhey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us riwayat ko Hatim bin Ismael ne apni taweel hadees mein musnad bayan kya hai (jabkey ye sanad mursal hai. Hatim ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se musnad bayan ki hai) aur Hatim ki riwayat ke musnad honey ki muwaafiqat Muhammad bin Ali Jaafi ne bhi ki hai aur Jaafar an abi an Jabir ki sanad se riwayat ki hai. farq itna hai ke Jaafi ne kaha : ( فصلى المغرب والعتمة بأذان وإقامة ( '' aapney maghrib aur Isha eik Azan aur eik iqaamat se padhi . Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke mujhey Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Hatim ne us taweel hadees mein khata ki hai."
1907,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan hai ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine yahan nahar kya hai aur Mina sarey ka sara qurban gah hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arafat mein waquf kya. to farmaya : ''maine yahan waquf kya hai aur sara Arafat jaey waquf hai.'' aapney Muzdalfa mein waquf kya aur farmaya : ''maine us jagah waquf kya hai aur tamam Muzdalfa jaey waquf hai.''
1908,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Janab Jaafar (Sadiq) (Rahimahullah) se unki sanad se riwayat kya, to mazeed kaha : '' to tum apney apney padaaw par nahar karo.''"
1909,Janab Jaafar (Sadiq) (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke mujhey merey walid ( Muhammad Baqar (Rahimahullah)) ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya. aur ye hadees bayan ki. aur apni hadees par واتخذوا من مقام إبراهيم مصلى ki jagah ye baat apni taraf se badhai ke aapney un rakaat mein toheed (yani ( ) قل هو الله أحد) aur sura Kafirun ki tilawat ki (ye jumla mudrij hai.) aur us mein bayan kya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye waqia Kufa mein bayan kya tha. merey walid (Muhammad bin Ali (Rahimahullah)) ne kaha ke Jabir ne ye lafz bhi nahin kahey they ke ''main ghussey ke aalim mein jaldi se gaya tha.'' aur Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ka qissa bayan kya.
1910,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Quraish aur unke ehle deen Muzdalfa mein waquf kya kartey they aur apney aap ko ''hims'' kahlaatey they. jabkey deegar sab arab Arafat mein waquf kartey they. bayan karti hain ke jab Islam aaya tu Allah taala ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hukm diya ke Arafat mein aa kar waquf karen, phir wahan se loten, chunanche yehi tafseer hai Allah taala ke us farman ki ثم أفيضوا من حيث أفاض الناس phir loto wahin se jahan se log laut-tey hain.''"
1911,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tarwiya ke roz (yani aathwin zil-Hijja ko) Zohar ki Namaz aur Arfa ke roz (nawin zil-Hijja ko) Fajr ki Namaz Mina mein padhi thi.
1912,"Abdul-Azeez bin Rafe kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke mujhey wo baat bataaiye jo aap ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yaad ho. tarwiya ke roz (aathwin zil-Hijja ko) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz kahan padhi thi ? unhoney kaha : Mina mein. maine kaha : nafr waley din (wapsi ke roz, 13 / zil-hijja ko) aapney Asr ki Namaz kahan padhi thi? unhoney kaha : wadi abtah ( mohsib ( mein . phir farmaya : wesay hi karo jaisey ke tumharey umra kartey hain."
1913,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arfa ke roz (naween taareekh ko) Mina mein subah ki Namaz padhaai , phir Arafat ki taraf aaye aur wadi namra mein padaaw kiya. wohi maqam jahan ke Arafat mein Imam utarta hai (unke daur ki baat hai) yahan tak ke jab Zohar ka waqt hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do-pehar ko garmi ke waqt hi mein wahan se rawana ho gaey aur Zohar aur Asr ki Namaz jama karkey padhaai, phir logon ko khutba diya, phir wahan se chaley aur Arafat mein apney thaharne ki jagah par ja kar thahre ."
1914,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke jab Hujjaj ne Hazrat (Abdullah) ibne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko Shahid kar diya to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchhwaa bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us din kis waqt yahan se chaltey they? unhoney kaha : jab waqt ho jaeyga ham chal paden gey. phir jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne chalney ka irada kiya to sathi boley : Suraj nahin dhalaa hai, phir puchha : kya dhal gaya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin dhalaa hai ya dhal gaya hai isliye jab unhoney kaha ke dhal gaya hai, to wo rawana ho gaey."
1915,Bani Zamra ka eik shakhs apney walid ya chacha se bayan karta hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Arafat ke roz member par dekha tha.
1916,Salma bin Nabeet apney qabeele ke eik shakhs se wo uskey walid Nabeet (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat karta hai ke usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Arafat mein waqoof kiye huey dekha. aap surkh oont par khutba dey rahey they.
1917,Janab Khalid bin Adaa bin Hauza (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Arfa ke roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney oont par uski rikaabon mein paon daley logon ko khutba dey rahey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne-al-Ula ne Wakee se usi tarah bayan kiya jaisey ke Hannaad ne kaha .
1918,Abdul-Majeed Abu-Amr ne Adaa bin Khalid se riwayat ki aur mazkura baala ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
1919,Hazrat Yazid bin Sheban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne Mirbbaa Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye jabkey ham Arafat mein aisi jagah waqoof kiye huey they ke Amr bin Abdullah usko Imam ke mauqif se door samajh rahey they. (ibne Mirbbaa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : be-shak main tumhari taraf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka paighaamber bin ke aaya hun. aapney tum logon ko kehla bheja hai : ''apney (inhi) maqamat par waqoof karo. bila-shuba tum apney Abba Ibrahim (Aleh.)  ki virasat mein se eik virasat par ho.''
1920,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Arafat se rawana huey to badey aaram aur sukoon se chaley. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey baithey huey they. aapney farmaya : ''logo ! aaram se chalo, neki ghodey aur oont daudhaaney mein nahin.'' so maine dekha ke (koi bhi sawari) apney dono (agley) paon utha kar na daudh rahi thi yahan tak ke aap Muzdalfa pahunch gaey . ... . Wahab ne mazeed kaha . ... . phir aapney Hazrat Fazal-bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko apney peechhey bitha liya aur farmaya : ''logo ! neki ghodey aur oont daudhaaney mein nahin, sukoon se chalo.'' aur maine nahin dekha ke koi sawari apney dono paon utha kar chal rahi ho. yahan tak ke aap Mina mein aagey."
1921,"Janab Kuraib bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : mujhey ye bataeyn ke us shaam jab aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey sawar they, aap logon ne kaisey kya? unhoney bataya ke ham us ghaati mein aaye jis mein log apni sawariyan bithaatey hain. wo jagah (معرس) kahlaati hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni oontni bithaai , phir peshab kiya. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne (أهراق الماء) ke lafz istimal nahin kiye. (yani ''pani bahaayaa'' nahin kaha.) phir aapney pani talab kiya aur wuzu farmaya jis mein koi mubaalgha na tha. (yani halka wuzu kya, ango ko eik do baar dhoya) maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Namaz? aapney farmaya : ''Namaz tumharey aagey hai.'' (aagey chal kar padhengey) phir aap Sawar ho gaey yahan tak ke ham Muzdalfa pahunch gaey . phir aapney maghrib ki Namaz padhaai . phir logon ne sawaariyon ko apney apney padaaw par bithaya magar unke (paalaan aur kajawey) nahin kholey yahan tak ke Isha ki iqaamat kahlwaai aur Namaz padhaai. phir logon ne (apni sawaariyon ko) khola. Muhammad bin Kaseer ne apni riwayat mein mazeed kaha : maine puchha : jab tum logon ne subah ki, to kaisey kya tha? unhoney kaha : fazal (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechhey sawar huey aur main Quraish ke un afrad ke sath pedal chala gaya jo deegar logon se pehley rawana huey they."
1922,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : phir aapney Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney peechhey sawar kar liya . phir aap apni oontni par darmiyani chaal (unuq) se rawana huey aur log daain baeyn oonton ko peet rahey they. aap unki taraf mutawajjeh na hotey they aur farma rahey they : ''logo ! sukoon ke sath !'' aur aap Arafat se Suraj ghuroob honey ke baad rawana huey."
1923,Janab Urwa (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha gaya. ... . aur main (is majlis mein) baitha tha. ... . ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hijjatul-wadaa mein jab Arfa se rawana huey they to kis raftaar se chaley they? unhoney kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) darmiyani raftaar (unuq) se chaley they. jab koi faraakhi (kushadgi) paatey to qadrey tez ho jatey. Hisham ne kaha ke (نص)  wali raftaar (عنق) se qadrey tez tar hoti hai.
1924,"Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey sawar tha, jab Suraj ghuroob ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wahan se rawana huey (yani Arafat se.)"
1925,"Kuraib maula Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna, wo keh rahey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Arafat se rawana huey yahan tak ke jab ghaati mein pahunchey to utrey , peshab kiya, phir wuzu kiya magar is mein mubaalgha nahin tha. maine arz kiya : Namaz? aapney farmaya : ''Namaz tumharey aagey hai.'' (yani aagey padhengey) phir aap Sawar ho gaey. jab Muzdalfa pahunchey , to utrey , wuzu kiya aur kamil wuzu kiya. phir Namaz ki iqaamat kahi gaee to maghrib ki Namaz padhaai, phir her shakhs ne apney apney oont ko apney apney padaaw mein bithaya , phir Isha ki iqaamat kahi gaee to aapney Namaz padhaai aur unke beech kuch nahin padha. Shareed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( Arafat sey) rawana hua tha, isliye aap ke qadmon ne zameen ko nahin chhua yahan tak ke Muzdalfa pahunch gaey."
1926,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen Muzdalfa mein ikhatti karkey padhin.
1927,Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat ki aur kaha : eik eik iqaamat se un dono namazon ko jama kiya.  Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Wakee ne bayan kiya ke aapney her Namaz (alag) iqaamat se padhi.
1928,Usman bin umr (Rahimahullah) ne ibne-abi Zi'ib se unhoney Zohri se yani Ahmed bin Hanbal ne Hammad ki sanad se aur uskey ham-maani bayan kiya ke har Namaz ke liye eik iqaamat kahi. aur pehli mein Azan nahin di aur na kisi ke baad sunnatein padhen. Mukhlid ne kaha : un mein se eik ke liye Azan nahin di.
1929,Abdullah bin Malik (bin Haris) bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath Namaz padhi . maghrib ki teen aur Isha ki do rakaten. Malik bin Haris ne un se kaha : ye kis tarah ki Namaz hai? unhoney kaha : maine unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath is jagah eik hi takbir ke sath padha hai.
1930,Saeed bin Jubair aur Abdullah bin Malik dono se riwayat hai ke ham ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath Muzdalfa mein maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen eik takbir ke sath padhin. aur Muhammad bin Kaseer ki riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya. (mazkura baala riwayat)
1931,Saeed bin Jubair ne kaha : ham Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath mein (Arafat sey) lautey. jab Muzdalfa pahunchey to unhoney hamein maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen teen rakaten aur do rakaten eik takbir ke sath padhaeen. jab farigh huey to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is jagah hamein isi tarah Namaz padhaai thi.
1932,Salma bin Kuhail ne kaha : maine Janab Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) ko Muzdalfa mein dekha ke unhoney iqaamat kahi aur maghrib ki teen rakaten padhein phir Isha ki do rakaten padhin. phir kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath hazir tha unhoney is jagah isi tarah kiya tha aur unhoney bayan kiya tha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha aur aapney is jagah isi tarah kiya tha.
1933,"Ash'as bin Sulaim apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath Arafat se Muzdalfa aaya . unhoney is dauran mein takbir aur tahleel ko nahin chhoda yahan tak ke ham Muzdalfa pahunch gaey. phir Azan aur iqaamat kahi ya kisi ko hukm diya ke Azan aur iqaamat kahe, phir hamein maghrib ki teen rakaten padhaaen, phir hamari taraf mutawajjeh huey aur kaha : Namaz , (Isha ki bhi.) isliye hamein Isha ki Namaz padhaai , do rakaten . phir apna raat ka khana talab kiya. (Ash'as bin Sulaim ne) kaha : mujhey Ilaj bin Amr ne isi tarah bayan kiya jaisey ke merey walid (Sulaim bin Aswad) ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kiya. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se is baarey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aisey hi padhi thi."
1934,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kabhi nahin dekha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi Namaz be-waqt padhi ho. aap hamesha waqt par Namaz padhtey they magar Muzdalfa mein aapney maghrib aur Isha ko jama karkey padha (takheer se). aur agley din ki Fajr ki Namaz apney waqt se pehley padhi.
1935,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (muzdalfa mein) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne subah ki aur quzah ke pahaad par waqoof kiya to farmaya : ''ye quzah hai aur jaey-waqoof hai. aur Muzdalfa sara hi jaey-waqoof hai. maine is jagah qurbani ki hai aur Mina sab hi qurban gaah hai. so apney apney padaaw par qurbaaniyaan karo.''
1936,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine Arafat mein is jagah par waqoof kiya hai aur Arafat sarey ka sara jaey-waqoof hai. maine Muzdalfa mein is jagah par waqoof kiya hai aur Muzdalfa sara hi jaey waqoof hai. aur maine is jagah qurbani ki hai aur Mina sab hi qurban gaah hai. isliye tum apney apney padaaw par qurbaaniyaan karo.''
1937,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Arafat sara hi maqame waqoof hai aur Mina sara hi qurban gaah hai aur Muzdalfa pura hi waqoof ki jagah hai. aur Makka ke sab raastey (yahan aaney ki) raah hain aur qurban gaah bhi.''
1938,Janab umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke ehale-jahiliyat (muzdalfa sey) us waqt tak rawana nahin hotey they jab tak ke pahaad sabeer par Suraj ko (tulu hota) na dekh letey. so Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki mukhalifat ki aur tulu aaftaab se pehley hi wahan se rawana ho liye.
1939,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehle ke un zaeef afrad mein shamil tha jin ko aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muzdalfa ki raat waqt se pehle rawana farma diya tha.
1940,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muzdalfa ki raat ham bani Abdul-Muttalib ke chhotey ladkon ko gadhon par Sawar karkey aagey bhej diya tha. is mauqe par aap hamari raanon par aahista aahista maartay huey farma rahey they : ''bacho ! Suraj tulu honey se pehley jamara ko kankariyaan na maarna. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain (اللطح) ka maani hai, naram andaz mein maarna.''"
1941,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ehle ke zaeef afrad ko andherey hi mein aagey rawana farma diya kartey they. aur unhen hukm detey they ke Suraj tulu honey tak jamara ko kankariyaan na maaren.
1942,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko nahar (qurbaani) wali raat Fajr se pehley hi (Mina ki janib) bhej diya. isliye unhoney (tulu) Fajr se pehley hi jamara ko kankariyaan maar lin phir wo chali gaeen aur tawafe-ifaaza kar liya. aur ye unhi ki baari ka din tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan they.
1943,Eik khabar deney waley ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Asma (binte-Abi Bakr) (Raziallahu anha) ne jamara ki rami ki to maine kaha : ham ne to raat mein rami ki hai. (kankariyaan maari hain) unhoney jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham yehi kiya kartey they.
1944,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (muzdalfa sey) rawana huey aur badey sukoon aur aaram se chaley. aur logon ko hukm diya ke chhoti chhoti kankariyaan maaren (magar) wadi mahsar mein se tezi se nikley they.
1945,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney hajj mein qurbani waley din jamaraa ke darmiyan khadey huey aur puchha : ''ye kon sa din hai? '' logon ne kaha : ye qurbani ka din hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Hajje-Akbar ka din hai.''
1946,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey un logon ke sath bheja jinhon ne qurbani ke roz Mina mein ye aelan kya tha ke is saal ke baad koi mushrik hajj ke liye na aaye . aur koi shakhs be-libas ho kar Baitullah ka tawaf na karey. aur qurbani ka din (Yomun-Nehar hai) Hajje-Akbar ka din hai. aur Hajje-Akbar se murad Hajj hai.
1947,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney hajj mein khutba detey huey irshad farmaya : ''bila-shuba zamana apni us ( asal ( kaiyfiyat par ghoom aaya hai) jis par ke apney pehley roz tha ( jabke Allah ne aasmano aur zameen ko paida farmaya tha. saal ke baara mahiney hain, aur un mein se chaar mahiney hurmat waley hain. teen mahiney mutawatir hain, yani zul-Qada , zul-hijja aur moharram aur chautha Muzar ka rajab hai jo jamaa dii aur shobaan (shabaan) ke darmiyan hota hai. ''"
1948,"Muhammad bin Sirin , ibne-Abi Bakra se wo (apney walid) abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne Aun ne naam lekar kaha ke Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakra (apney walid) Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain."
1949,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar Deli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke aap maidane-Arafat mein they. usi dauran mein Najad ki taraf ke kuchh log aaye aur unhoney eik shakhs ko kaha to usney pukar kar kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hajj kaisey hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (bhi) eik shakhs ko hukm diya aur usney pukar kar kaha : ''hajj : hajj Arafat ka din hai. jo shakhs Muzdalfa ki raat mein Fajr ki Namaz se pehley pehley yahan aa gaya uska hajj pura ho gaya. Mina ke din teen hain. jo shakhs do din baad jaldi se wapis ho jaey us par koi gunah nahin aur jo takheer karey (teesra din bhi waqoof karey) to us par bhi koi gunah nahin.'' phir aapney apney peechhey eik shakhs ko sawar kara liya jo is baat ki manadi kerney laga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Mehraan ne Sufiyan se aisey hi riwayat kiya hai (الحج الحج) (yani) do baar. jabkey Yahya bin Saeed Qataan ne Sufiyan se ye lafz (الحج) eik baar bayan kiya hai.
1950,Hazrat Urwa bin Muzris Taai (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Muzdalfa mein waqoof ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main qabeela tey ke do pahadon se aaya hun. maine apni sawari ko halkaan kiya hai aur apney aap ko bahut thakaaya hai. qasam Allah ki ! maine koi teela (ya pahad) nahin chhoda magar us par waqoof kiya hai. to kya mera hajj ho gaya? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney hamarey sath ye Namaz (Fajr) pa li aur is se pehley wo raat ya din mein Arafat mein hazir ho chuka hai to uska hajj pura ho gaya aur usney apna mail kuchail door kar liya. (us ne manaasik hajj purey kar liye. ab uskey baad ke deegar aamaale hajj purey karkey apna ehram khol dey.'')
1951,"Abdur-Rehman bin Muaz (Rahimahullah) eik sahabi se bayan kartey hain, usney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mina mein logon ko khutba diya aur unhen apney apney maqamat par utarney ka irshad farmaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''muhajrin yahan padaaw keren.'' aur qible ki janib daain taraf ishara farmaya.'' aur ansaar yahan padaaw keren.'' aur qible ki baain taraf ishara farmaya.'' aur deegar log unke ird-gird utren.''"
1952,"Ibne-Abi Najeeh apney walid sey, wo Banu-Bakr ke do aadmiyon se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney bayan kiya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ayyaame-tashreeq ke darmiyani din mein khutba detey huey dekha. ham aap ki sawari ke qarib hi they aur ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wo khutba tha jo aapney Mina mein irshad farmaya."
1953,Rabeea bin Abdur-Rehman bin Husain apni daadi Saraa binte Nabhaan (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain. ... . ye khatoon qabl az Islam (Islam se pahle) eik ghar ki nigraan thin (jis mein but hua kartey they) . ... . wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ruoos waley din hamein khutba diya. aapney farmaya : ''ye kon sa din hai? '' ham ne kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Abu-Hurra Raqaashi ke chacha ne bhi aisey hi riwayat kiya hai ke aapney tashreeq ke dinon ke darmiyani din mein khutba diya.
1954,Hazrat Harmaas bin Ziyad Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Mina mein qurbani waley din apni azbaa oontni par logon ko khutba dey rahey they.
1955,Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Mina mein qurbani waley din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khutba suna .
1956,Janab Raafe bin Amr Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap Mina mein apney safed khachchar par logon ko khutba dey rahey they jabkey din ooncha aa chuka tha aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki baat aagey pahuncha rahey they. log kuchh baithey they aur kuchh khadey they.
1957,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Muaz Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein khutba diya jabkey ham Mina mein they. isliye (Allah tabarak w taala ne) hamarey kaan khol diye, ham apney apney padaaw par they aur wo sab kuchh sun rahey they jo aap farma rahey they. aap hamein aamaale-hajj ki taaleem farma rahey they yahan tak ke jamaraat tak pahunch gaey, to aapney apni shahadat ki ungliyan (apney kanon mein) rakhin aur farmaya : ''chhoti chhoti kankariyaan maaro.'' aapney muhajrin ko hukm diya to wo masjid (khaif) ke aagey ki taraf utrey. aur ansaar ko hukm diya to wo masjid se peechhey ki taraf utrey. phir doosrey log unke baad utrey."
1958,"Abdur-Rehman bin Farukh ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke ham logon ke sath kharid aur farokht kartey hain, to ham mein se koi Makka bhi aa jata hai aur apney maal ke sath raat guzaarta hai to unhoney jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne to raaten Mina mein guzari thin aur din bhi."
1959,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki thi ke logon ko pani pilaney ki gharz se Mina ki raaten Makka mein guzar len to aapney unko ijazat de-di thi.
1960,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mina mein chaar rakaten padhein to Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath do do rakaten (qasr) padhi hain. (Musaddad ne) Hafs bin Ghiyas se mazeed ye bhi kaha : aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi, ke wo ibtidaai (shuruati) daure-khilaafat mein (qasr kartey rahey) phir aakhir mein wo puri padhney lagey they. (Musaddad ne) yahan se Abu-Muaawia se ye izafa kiya ke (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha :) phir tumhari raahen mukhtalif ho gaeen aur mujhey do rakaten jo (Allah ke yahan) qubul ho jaeyn chaar rakaaton se behtar maloom hoti hain. Aamash ne kaha : mujhey Muawiya bin Qurra ne apney buzurgon (asaatza) se bayan kiya ke Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi chaar rakaten padhein to un se kaha gaya ke aap Usman (Raziallahu anhu) par aib lagatey hain phir bhi chaar padhtey hain? kehney lagey : ikhtilaf karna bura kaam hai."
1961,Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mina mein chaar rak'aat isliye padhi thin ke unhoney hajj ke baad wahin iqaamat ka azm kar liya tha.
1962,Janab Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke chaar rakaat padhney ki wajeh ye thi ke unhoney usey watan bana liya tha. (yahan unhoney shaadi kar li thi.)
1963,Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab taaif main apni jaaidaad ley li aur yahan iqaamat ka irada kar liya to chaar rakaten padhin. unke baad deegar aimma (bani Umayya) ne yehi amal ikhtiyar kar liya.
1964,Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mina mein badwi logon ki wajeh se puri Namaz padhi thi kyonkey wo us saal bahut kaseer tadaad mein aaye they to unhoney logon ko chaar rakaten padhaeen taake un badviyon ko maloom rahey ke Namaz chaar rak'aat hai.
1965,Hazrat Harisa bin Wahab Khuzaai (Raziallahu anhu) . ... . ki maa Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki zojiyat mein thi aur un se unka beta Ubaidullah bin umr paida hua tha. ... . Harisa ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Mina mein Namaz padhi. logon ki tadaad bahut ziyada thi to aapney hamein Hijjatul-wadaa mein do rakaten padhaeen. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Harisa qabeela khuza'a ke fard they aur unka ghar Makka mein tha.
1966,Sulaiman bin Amr bin Al Ahwas ki walida bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wadi ke darmiyan se jamara ko kankariyaan maartey dekha jabke aap sawari par they. aap her kankari ke sath (الله اكبر) kehtey they. eik shakhs aap ke peechhey se aap ko chhupaey huey tha. maine us shakhs ke mutalliq puchha to kaha : Fazal-bin Abbas hain. logon ne bahut bheed kar di to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo ! eik doosrey ko qatl mat karo. aur jab tum jamre ko kankariyaan maaro to chhoti chhoti maaro.''
1967,Sulaiman bin Amr bin Al Ahwas ki walida ka bayan hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jamara Aqba ke paas dekha. aap sawari par they. maine aap ki ungliyon mein kankariyaan dekhin. aapney wo maarin to phir aur logon ne bhi maarin .
1968,Yazid bin Abi Ziyad ne apni sanad se usi ke misl riwayat kiya aur izafa kiya ke aap jamara ke paas rukey nahin.
1969,Naafe (Rahimahullah) ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke mutalliq bataya ke wo qurbani ke din (yani das zil-hijja) ke baad teen dino mein jamaraat ke paas pedal hi aatey jatey they aur bayan kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kiya kartey they.
1970,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap qurbani waley din apni sawari par se kankariyaan maar rahey they aur farmatey they : ''mujh se apney aamaale-hajj seekh lo , main nahin janta , shayad main apney is hajj ke baad hajj na kar sakoon.''"
1971,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap qurbani waley din chaasht ke waqt apni sawari par se rami kar rahey they. magar uskey baad ke dino mein Suraj dhalney ke baad ki."
1972,"Wabra (bin Abdur-Rehman Sulmee) kehtey hain, maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke main kis waqt jamaraat ko kankariyaan maarun? unhoney kaha : jab tumhara Imam maarey tum bhi maar lo. maine apna sawal dohraayaa to boley : ham Suraj dhalney ka intizar kiya kartey they. jab Suraj dhal jata to rami kartey they (qurbani waley din ke baad ke dinon (din) mein.)"
1973,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (das taareekh ko qurbani waley din) Zohar padh leney ke baad din ke aakhiri hissey mein tawafe-ifaaza kiya. phir aap Mina laut aaye. aur  tashreeq ke dinon ki raaten yahin thehrey rahey. Suraj dhalney ke baad jamaraat ko kankariyaan maartey they. har jamre ko saat kankariyaan maartey aur her kankari ke sath (الله اكبر) kehtey. pehley aur doosrey jamre ke paas kafi lambi der rukte aur apni aajizi aur tazraa ka izhar kartey (duaen kartey) phir teesrey jamre ko kankariyaan maartey magar uskey paas nahin rukte they.
1974,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jamara kubraa (Jamara Aqba) ke paas pahunchey to aapney Baitullah ko apney baain janib aur Mina ko daain janib kiya aur phir jamre ko saat kankariyaan maarin. Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur is tarah se rami ki us zaat ne jis par Sura Baqara nazil ki gaee thi.
1975,"Abul-Badaah bin Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oonton ke charwaahon ko Mina mein raaten guzaarney se rukhsat di thi (ke) ye log qurbani waley din rami karen, phir agley din (gyaarahwin taareekh ko) uskey baad aglaa din chhod kar rawangi waley din do din ki rami karen."
1976,Abul-Badaah bin Adi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne charwaahon ko rukhsat di thi ke eik din rami keren aur eik din chhod den.
1977,Abu-Mujliz bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se rami-jimaar ke baarey mein puchha tha to unhoney kaha : mujhey maloom nahin ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chhe kankariyaan maari thin ya saat.
1978,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi (daswin taareekh ko) jamara Aqba ki rami kar ley to uskey liye biwiyon ke siwa her cheez halal ho gaee.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : ye hadees zaeef hai. Hujjaj (bin Irtaat) ne Zohri ko na dekha hai aur na us se kuchh suna hai."
1979,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon par rehem farma.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur katarwaane walon ke liye bhi (dua farmaeyn.) aapney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! sar mundwaaney walon par rehem farma'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool aur katarwaane walon ke liye bhi, tab aapney farmaya : ''aur baal katarwaane walon par bhi (reham farma).''"
1980,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hijjatul-Wadaa mein apna sar mundwaya tha.
1981,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani waley din jamara Aqba ko kankariyaan maarin , phir Mina main apni manzil par tashrif laye, phir apni qurbani talab ki aur usey zibeh kiya, phir hajjaam ko bulwaya aur usney aap ke sar ke daain janib ko liya aur usey moondaa. to aapney apney paas walon ko eik eik do do baal taqseem kar diye. phir usney baain janib ko liya aur usey moonda to aapney farmaya : ''Abu-Talha yahan hai?'' chunanche wo Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko dey diye."
1982,Sufiyan ne Hisham bin Hassaan se apni sanad se ye hadees bayan ki. is mein hai ke aapney hajjaam se farmaya : ''meri daain janib se shuru karo aur (pehley) usey moondo.''
1983,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Mina ke dinon mein sawalat kiye jatey they aur aap farmatey they : ''koi harj nahin.'' eik shakhs ne sawal kartey huey kaha : maine qurbani se pehley baal moond liye hain. aapney farmaya : ''qurbani karo aur koi harj nahin.'' eik ne kaha : maine shaam kar di hai aur rami nahin ki hai. aapney farmaya : ''rami karo aur koi harj nahin.''
1984,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton ke liye sar mundaanaa nahin hai. unke liye sirf baal kutarnaa hai.''"
1985,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton ke liye sar mundaanaa nahin hai. unke liye sirf baal kutarnaa hai.''"
1986,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj se pehley Umra kiya tha.
1987,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke qasam Allah ki ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ko Zil-hijja mein sirf isliye Umra karaya tha ke us se ehle shirk ka amal batil karen. bila-shuba qabeela Quraish aur unke ehale-deen kaha kartey they ke jab oonton ke baal badh jaeyn, unke zakhm theek ho jaeyn aur maah safar shuru ho jaey to Umra karney waley ke liye Umra karna halal ho gaya. ye log un dinon mein Umra karney ko haram kehtey they yahan tak ke zul-hijja aur muhrram guzar jaey."
1988,"Abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke mujhey Marwan ke is paigham lane wale ne khabar di jis ko usney Umme-Maaqil (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan bheja tha. Umme-Maaqil (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Abu-Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hajj ke liye nikley. jab wo aaye to Umme-Maaqil ne kaha : tum jantey ho ke mujh par (bhi) hajj (lazim) hai. chunanche wo dono chaltey aaye yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se miley. isliye Umme-Maaqil (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! bila-shuba mujh par hajj farz hai aur Abu-Maaqil ke paas sirf eik oont hai. Abu-Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey : ye sach kehti hai aur maine us oont ko Allah ki raah mein kar diya hai (jihad mein). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ye usey do, ye is par hajj karegi, ye bhi Allah ke raste mein hai.'' chunanche Abu-Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye oont usey dey diya. to wo kehney lagi : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aurat zaat hun, umr ziyada ho gaee hai aur bimar bhi hun, to kya koi amal aisa hai jo mujh se merey hajj se kifaayat kar jaey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ramazan mein Umra, hajj se kifaayat karta hai.''"
1989,"Hazrat Umme-Maaqil (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa kiya to hamarey paas eik hi oont tha. Abu-Ma'aqil (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko jihad fi sabeel Allah ke liye waqf kar diya tha. hamein bimari ne aa liya aur Abu-Ma'aqil faut ho gaey. aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley gaey . jab aap apney hajj se farigh ho kar aaye to main khidmat mein hazir hui . aapney farmaya : ''aey Umme- Maaqil ! kya rukawat thi ke to hamarey sath hajj ke liye nahin gaee?'' usney kaha : ham to tayyar they magar Abu-Ma'aqil faut ho gaey, hamara eik hi oont tha jis par hamein hajj karna tha, to Abu-Ma'aqil ne uskey baarey mein wasiyat kar di ke ye jihad fi sabeel Allah ke liye waqf hai. aapney farmaya : ''to usi par kyon na chal di? bila-shuba hajj ''fi sabeel Allah'' hi hai. khair jab tum se hamarey sath ye hajj karna faut ho gaya hai to Ramazan mein Umra karna, bila-shuba ye hajj ki manind hai.'' chunanche wo kaha karti thin ke hajj hajj hai aur Umra umrah hai. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se ye farmaya tha, maloom nahin ye baat merey liye khas thi (ya ummat ke liye aam.)"
1990,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajj ka irada farmaya to eik aurat ne apney shohar se kaha : mujhey bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath apney oont par hajj karao. usney kaha : merey paas koi aisi sawari nahin jis par main tumhen hajj karaaoon. aurat ne kaha : apney falan oont par? usney jawab diya ke wo to fi-sabee-lillah (jihad ke liye) waqf hai. isliye wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga ke meri biwi ne aap ko ''السلام علیکم ورحمۃ اللہ '' kaha hai, aur wo mujhey kehti hai ke main usko aap ke sath hajj karaaoon. wo kehti hai : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein hajj karao. to maine us se kaha : merey paas koi sawari nahin jis par main tujhey hajj karaaoon. usney kaha : apney falan oont par . to maine kaha : wo to fi-sabee-lillah waqf hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum usey us par hajj kara do to ye bhi fi-sabee-lillah hi hai.'' usney kaha ke us (aurat) ne mujhey kaha hai ke main aap se ye daryaft karun ke kon sa amal aap ke sath hajj ke barabar ho sakta hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey (meri taraf sey) ''السلام علیکم ورحمۃ اللہ و برکاتہ'' kehna aur usey batana ke Ramazan mein Umra karna merey sath hajj kerney ke barabar hai.''"
1991,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do Umerey kiye they eik zul-Qada mein aur eik Shawwaal mein.
1992,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kitney Umerey kiye? unhoney kaha : do . Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anha) ko to maloom hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen Umerey kiye they, siwaye uskey jisey aapney Hajjatul-wadaa ke sath mila kar kiya tha."
1993,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar Umerey kiye they. Umra Hudebiya (jis se aap ko wapis jana pada tha). doosra wo jo hasab ittifaq muahida agley saal kiya. teesra ja'araana se aur chautha jo aapney apney hajj ke sath mila kar kiya.
1994,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaar Umerey kiye they aur sabhi zul-Qada mein kiye, siwaye uskey jo hajj ke sath tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain yahan tak mujhey Hudba bin Khalid se khoob yaad hai. aur Abul-Waleed se bhi maine suna hai magar achhi tarah zabt nahin. yani Umrae-Hudebiya ke zamaney mein , Umratul-qazaa zul-Qada mein , Umrae-ja'araana jab aapney zul-Qada mein Hunain ki ghaneematein taqseem ki thin aur hajj ke sath wala Umra."
1995,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is se farmaya tha : ''aey Abdur-Rehman ! apni behan Aaisha ko apney peechhey sawar karo aur usey tan'eem se Umra karwa lao. tum jab usey lekar tiley se nichey utro to usey chahiye ke ehram baandhey. be-shak ye Umra maqbool hoga.''
1996,"Hazrat Muhrish ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ja'araana mein tashrif laye, phir masjid mein aaye aur jo Allah ne chaha Namaz padhi . phir aapney ehram baandha , phir apni sawari par durust ho kar baith gaey aur daman wadi sarf ka rukh kar liya yahan tak ke Madina ki raah par ja miley aur Makka mein subah ki, goya ke aap raat hi se yahin they."
1997,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Umrae-qaza mein (Makka ke andar) teen din thehrey they.
1998,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani waley din tawafe-ifaaza kiya, phir laut kar Mina mein Zohar ki Namaz padhi."
1999,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke qurbani waley din shaam ko meri baari ki raat thi , jis mein ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko merey paas tashrif lana tha. chunanche aap tashrif laye aur merey paas Wahab bin Zam-aa aaya aur uskey sath aale abi Umayya ka eik aur aadmi bhi tha. un dono ne qameesen pehan rakhi thin , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Wahab se farmaya : ''Abu-Adbullah ! kya tum ne tawafe-ifaaza kar liya hai? '' usney kaha : nahin, qasam Allah ki ! aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni ye qamis utaar do.'' chunanche usney apni qamis utaar di aur sar ki janib se utaari. aur uskey sathi ne bhi utaar di , aur sar ki janib se utaari. phir unhoney puchha : aur ye kyon aey Allah ke Rasool? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba tumhen us din mein rukhsat (chhoot) hai ke jab tum jamara ko kankariyaan maar lo to halal ho jao. yani her us chiz se jo tum par haram ki gaee hai, siwaye biwiyon ke. agar Baitullah ka tawaf kerney se pehley shaam ho jaey to tum phir se mohrim ho jaogey jaisey ke kankariyaan maarney se pehley they yahan tak ke uska tawaf kar lo.''"
2000,Hazrat Aaysha aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke roz tawaf ko raat tak muakhkhar (der) kiya tha.
2001,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney tawafe-ifaaza mein ramal nahin kiya tha ( aahista aahista nahin daurey they jaisey ke tawafe-qudoom mein kiya tha).
2002,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) farmatey hain ke log (hajj ke baad) har janib wapis chaley jatey they. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs hergiz na jaey yahan tak ke uska aakhiri amal Baitullah ka tawaf ho.''
2003,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Safiya binte (Huyi) (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr kiya to bataya gaya ke usey haiz aa gaya hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad ye hamein rokney wali hai?'' (ghar walon ne) kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney tawafe-ifaaza kar liya hai. to aapney farmaya : ''tab nahin.''
2004,"Hazrat Haris bin Abdullah bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur un se puchha ke jo aurat qurbani waley din tawaf kar chuki ho, phir usey haiz aa jaey to? umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : chahiye ke uska aakhiri amal Baitullah ka tawaf ho. tab Haris ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi mujh se aisey hi farmaya tha. to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ''terey haath gir jaeyn. mujh se wo baat poochhtey hai jo pehley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochh chuka hai taake main unki mukhalifat karun.''"
2005,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine tan'eem se Umerey ka ehram baandha , phir Haram mein dakhil hui aur apna Umra pura kiya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wadi abtah mein mera intizar kiya yahan tak ke main farigh ho gaee. aur aapney logon ko kooch kerney ka hukm diya aur kehti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baitullah mein tashrif laye, uska tawaf kiya phir rawana ho gaey."
2006,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Mina se aakhiri din mein nikli to aapney wadi mohsib mein padaaw kiya. (Makka aur Mina ke darmiyan maqbara ma'alaa se Mina ki taraf janey waley raastey ka naam abtah aur mohsib hai.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne Bashaar ne is hadees mein unko tan'eem ki taraf rawana kerney ka zikr nahin kiya. (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha)) kehti hain : chunanche main sahar ke waqt (umrey se farigh ho kar) aap ke paas pahunchi to aapney Sahaba ko kooch ka hukm diya aur khud sawar huey aur Namaze-Fajr se pehley Baitullah mein aaye , tawaf kiya aur phir Madina ki raah ki taraf chal nikley."
2007,Abdur-Rehman bin Tariq apni walida se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Yaala ke ghar se aagey badhtey to Baitullah ki taraf rukh kartey aur dua farmatey. Ubaidullah wo jagah bhool gaey they.
2008,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wadi mohsib mein isliye utrey they taake aap ko (Makka sey) nikalney mein aasani rahey. ye koi mashroo'a (sharaee) sunnat nahin hai. jo chahey yahan utar jaey aur jo chahey na utrey.
2009,Hazrat Abu-Raafe (maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey ye hukm nahin diya tha ke main aap ke padaaw ka yahan intizam karun lekin maine (apney taur par) yahan aap ka khema laga diya tha to aap yahan utar padey they. Janab Musaddad ne kaha ke abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samane-safar ke nigraan aur muntazim they. Usman bin abi Sheba ne apni riwayat mein (في الأبطح) ka lafz zikr kiya hai.
2010,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke hajj ke mauqe par maine puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kal kahan qiyam farmaeyn gey? aapney farmaya : ''bhala Aqeel ne hamarey liye koi manzil rehney bhi di hai?'' phir aapney kaha : ''ham khaif bani kinaana mein qiyam karengey , jahan quraishiyon ne kufr par aapas mein muahida kiya tha. '' yani wadi mohsib mein. aur iski tafsil ye hai ke bani kinaana ne quraishiyon ke sath bani haashim ke khilaf ye qasmen uthai thin ke un se nikah shaadi karengey na kharid aur farokht aur na unhen koi jagah dengey. Zohri ne kaha : ''Khaif'' wadi hai."
2011,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab Mina se rawangi ka irada kiya to farmaya : ''ham kal (khaif bani kinaana mein) utren gey.'' aur mazkura baala ki manind zikr kiya. magar (Auzaai ne) riwayat ka pehla hissey (Usama ka sawal jawab) zikr nahin kiya aur na ''Khaif'' ka ke ye wadi hai.
2012,"Janab Naafe (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke (Mina se wapsi par) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Bat'haa (abtah / mohsib) mein zara der sotey, phir Makka mein dakhil hotey. aur kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aisey hi kiya kartey they. (yani tawafe-wadaa' kiya kartey they.)"
2013,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bat'haa mein Zohar , Asr , maghrib aur Isha ki namaazen padhein , phir kuchh der soey , phir Makka mein dakhil huey . aur ibne-Umar aisey hi kiya kartey they."
2014,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par Mina mein waqoof kiya to log aap se masayel daryaft kartey they. eik shakhs aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey maloom nahin ho saka aur maine zibeh kerney se pehley apney baal mundwaa liye? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zibeh kar lo, koi harj nahin.'' eik doosra aaya aur bola : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey maloom nahin ho saka aur maine rami kerney se pehley qurbani kar li? aapney farmaya : ''rami kar lo , koi harj nahin.'' kehtey hain ke us din aap se jo sawal bhi hua jis mein koi taqdeem takheer hui thi. aapney yehi farmaya : ''kar lo , koi harj nahin.''"
2015,"Hazrat Usama bin Shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hajj ke liye rawana hua. log aap ke paas aatey they, to jisney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine tawaf se pehley saee kar li hai ya koi kaam pehley kar liya hai ya koi muakhkhar kar diya hai. to aap farmatey they : ''koi harj nahin. koi harj nahin. magar jo koi zulm kartey huey kisi musalman ki izzat ko kaatey. (gheebat karey ya ta'an aur tashneea' waghaira) to wo harj mein pada aur halak hua.''"
2016,"Kasir bin Kasir ke dada ( Hazrat Matlab bin Abi Wdaa'a (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (masjide haram mein) baab bani saham ke paas Namaz padhtey dekha jabke log aap ke aagey se guzar rahey they aur unke darmiyan ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Kaaba ke beech) sutarah nahin tha. Sufiyan ne basaraahat (wazahat ke sath) kaha : (ليس بينه وبين الكعبة سترة * * *)  Sufiyan kehtey hain ke ibne-Juraij ne iski sanad mein yun bayan kiya tha, (أخبرنا كثير  عن أبيه) ''yani kaseer ne apney walid se bayan kiya, phir maine un se (barahe-rast) puchha to kaha : maine ye hadees apney walid se nahin suni balke ghar ke kisi doosrey fard se suni thi aur usney merey dada se riwayat ki hai."
2017,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Allah taala ne jab apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye Makka Fateh kara diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un (ehale-Makka) mein khadey huye, Allah taala ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki phir farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne Makka se haathi ko rok liya tha magar apney Rasool aur momineen ko is par ghalib farma diya hai. aur ye shehar merey liye din ke eik hissey mein (qitaal ke liye) halal kiya gaya hai. phir uskey baad qiyamat tak ke liye haram hai. uskey darkht na kaatey jaeyn , uska shikar na daudaayaa jaey aur na uski giri padi chiz ko uthana hai, siwaey iske ke koi uska aelan karey (to utha ley).'' Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! magar izkhir ghaas (ki ijazat ho) ye hamari qabron aur gharon mein istimal hoti hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''magar izkhir.'' (us ka kaatna mabaah (jayez)) hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibne Masfee ne Waleed se mazeed bayan kiya ke phir Abu-Shah (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey . ... jo ehale Yaman mein se they. ... . aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey likhwa dijiye. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Shah ke liye likh do.'' (Waleed kehtey hain ke) maine Imam Auzaai (Rahimahullah) se puchha ke ''Abu-Shah ke liye likh do.'' is se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : yehi khutba jo unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha."
2018,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se is qisse mein marwi (bayan) hai, farmaya : (ولا يُخْتَلَى خَلَاهَا) yani iski ghaas na kaati jaey."
2019,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai, kehti hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham aap ke liye Mina mein ghar na bana den. ya kaha koi imarat na bana den jo aap ko dhoop se bachaey? to aapney farmaya : ''nahin, ye theherney ka maqam hai aur har us shakhs ke liye hai jo pehley aa jaey."
2020,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Haram mein ghalley ka zakhira karna (logon se roke rakhna) ilhaad (be-deeni) hai.''"
2021,"Bakr bin Abdullah se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha : us ghar ke khuddam (sewak) ko kya hua hai ke ye log nabeez pilaatey hain (khajoor ya kishmish ka sharbat) jabke inke chacha zaad (Quraish) doodh , shehad aur sattu pilaatey hain? kya ye bakheel hain ya mohtaj? to ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne jawab diya. ham bakheel hain na mohtaj. darasal jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni sawari par tashrif laye they aur unke peechhey Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu Anhuma) baithey huey they to aapney peeney ko kuchh talab kiya to unhen nabeez pesh ki gaee thi. aapney us mein se pee aur baqi Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko de-di , unhoney bhi us se pee. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne bahut khoob kiya, bahut achchhaa kiya, so aisey hi kiya karo.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo farma diya hai usko ham badalna nahin chahtey."
2022,"Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ne Saaib bin Yazid se puchha : kya aapney Makka mein iqaamat ke baarey mein kuchh suna hai? to unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Ala bin Hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha, aap farmatey they : ''Muhajir log tawafe-sadr (ifaaza) ke baad teen din tak ruk saktey hain.''"
2023,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Usama bin Zaid , Usman bin Talha Al Hajbi aur Bilal (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) Kaaba ke andar dakhil huey aur Bilal ne darwaza band kar diya. isliye aap (kuchh der) andar rahey. Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke maine Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se unke nikalney par puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne andar kya kiya tha? unhoney bataya ke aapney eik sutoon apni baain janib kiya aur do sutoon daain janib aur teen sutoon apney peechhey aur phir Namaz padhi. aur Baitullah un dino chhe sutonon par qaaim tha."
2024,"Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne ye hadees riwayat ki magar sutonon ka zikr nahin kiya, kaha : phir aapney Namaz padhi . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur qible ki deewar ke darmiyan teen haath ka fasla tha."
2025,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se naqal kartey hain. aur Qaanabi ki (mazkura baala) riwayat ki manind bayan kiya. kaha : main ye poochhnaa bhool gaya ke aapney kitni rakaten padhin?
2026,Abdur-Rehman bin Safwan kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Kaaba mein dakhil huey to kya kiya tha? unhoney kaha : aapney do rakaten padhi thin.
2027,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Makka mein tashrif laye to Kaaba ke andar janey se inkar farma diya kyonkey uskey andar but rakhey huey they. chunanche aapney hukm diya aur unhen bahir nikal diya gaya. un mein Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) aur Ismael Alehissalam ki taswiren bhi thin jinkey haathon mein paansey (qismat maloom kerney ke teer) dikhlaaye gaey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah un par lanat karey, qasam Allah ki ! unhen khoob ilm tha ke in hazraat ne kabhi bhi in se paansey nahin daley they.'' chunanche iskey baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Kaaba mein dakhil huey aur uskey atraaf (aas-pas) aur konon mein takbeeren kahin. phir aap nikal aaye aur andar Namaz nahin padhi."
2028,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main chahti thi ke Kaaba ke andar dakhil houn aur is mein Namaz padhun, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mera haath pakda aur Hajar (yani hateem) mein dakhil kar diya aur farmaya : ''jab tum Kaaba mein dakhil hona chaho to Hajar mein Namaz padh liya karo, ye bhi Baitullah hi ka hissa hai. haqeeqat ye hai ke teri qaum ne taameere-Kaaba ke waqt isi qadr par iktifa kiya (kafi samjha) aur isey taameer se khaarij kar diya tha.''"
2029,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan se tashrif ley gaey to bahut masroor aur khush they. phir merey yahan wapis lautey to kisi qadr kabeeda aur ranjeedah se they. aur farmaya : ''main Kaaba mein dakhil hua hun agar mujhey apney is maamley ka pehley ilm hota jo baad mein maloom hua hai to main iskey andar dakhil na hota . mujhey andesha hai ke maine apni ummat par mashaqqat dali hai.''
2030,"Mansoor Hajabi se marwi (bayan) hai ke mujhey merey mamu (Musaafea' bin Sheba) ne meri walida Safiya binte Sheba se riwayat kiya, wo kehti hain ke maine Aslamiya se suna, kehti thin ke maine Usman (bin Talha al Hajbi) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab tumhen bulaya tha to kya farmaya tha? unhoney kaha : aapney farmaya tha : ''main tujhey ye kehna bhool gaya tha ke do seengon ko dhanp do , Baitullah mein koi aisi chiz nahin honi chahiye jo namazi ko mashghool kerney wali ho. ibne Sarah ne apni sanad mein ''(حدثني khaali)'' ke baad ''(Musaafea' bin Shaiba)'' ke naam ki tasreeh (wazahat) ki hai."
2031,"Hazrat Sheba bin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) usi jagah baithey huey they jahan tum baithey ho to unhoney kaha : main yahan se nahin niklun ga yahan tak ke Kaabe ka maal taqseem kar dun. Sheba kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aap ye nahin kar saktey. unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, main zarur karunga. maine kaha : aap nahin kar saktey. kehney lagey : kyon? maine kaha : bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is maal ki khabar thi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi ilm tha aur wo is maal ke aap se ziyada zarurat mand they magar unhoney isey nahin nikala. chunanche wo uthey aur chaley gaey."
2032,"Hazrat Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath maqame-liyaa se wapis lautey aur sidra (beri) ke paas pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Qarne-Aswad ke paas ruk gaey. yani us pahad ke paas jo is beri ke samney hai. phir aapney maqame-nakhab ki taraf nazar uthai ya uski wadi ki taraf dekha. aap rukey yahan tak ke sab log ruk gaey, tab aapney farmaya : ''wadi vaj ka shikar aur uskey kaante-daar darkht haram hain aur Allah ki khatir haram kiye gaey hain.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye irshad aap ke taaif janey aur saqif ka muhaasra (ghaira bandi) kerney se pehley ka hai."
2033,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paalaan na kasey (yani safar na kiye) jaeyn magar teen masaajid ki taraf , yani masjide haram (Baitullah) meri ye masjid (masjide-nabawi) aur masjide-aqsaa ki taraf.''"
2034,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kuchh nahin likha hai siwaye Quran karim ke aur jo is sahifey mein hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''Madina Munawwara Aair aur Saur (do pahadon) ke beech Haram hai. to jo yahan koi bidat nikaley ya kisi bid'ati ko jagah dey , us par Allah , farishton aur sab logon ki lanat ho. uska farz aur nafl kuchh qubul nahin hoga. musalmanon ka zimma (kisi kafir ko diya hua ehado-aman, ijtimae taur par) eik hi hai. unka adnaa fard bhi uski hifazat ke liye koshish ka paband hai. jisney kisi musalman ke diye huey ehado-aman ko toda to us par Allah , farishton aur sab logon ki lanat hai. uska farz aur nafl kuchh qubul nahin hoga. aur jo ( azad shuda ghulam ( apney azad kerney walon ki ijazat ke baghair kisi aur qaum ki taraf apney azad honey ki nisbat karey, us par Allah aur sab farishton ki lanat hai. us se koi farz aur nafl qubul nahin hoga.''"
2035,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne mazkura baala qisse mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kiya ke aapney farmaya : ''iski ghaas na kaati jaey, iska shikar na bhagaayaa jaey, iski giri-padi chiz na uthai jaey magar wo jo uska aelan karey. kisi ko munasib nahin ke qitaal ki gharz se is mein aslaha uthaey. aur kisi ko munasib nahin ke is se darkht kaatey magar koi apney oont ko chaara dena chahey to jayez hai.''"
2036,"Hazrat Adi bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina munawwara ki her taraf se eik eik bareed ( baara , baara meel ( ko mehfooz ilaaqa qarar diya tha ke na iskey darkht kaatey jaeyn aur na pattey todey jaeyn , magar oont ke chaarey ke ba-qadr jayez hai."
2037,"Sulaiman bin abi Abdullah bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney Haram Madina mein , jisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Haram qarar diya hai, eik aadmi ko shikar kartey pakad liya aur uskey kapdey chheen liye to us shakhs (ghulam) ke Malik aaye aur iskey baarey mein baat ki to unhoney kaha : bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko Haram qarar diya hai aur farmaya hai : ''jo shakhs kisi ko is mein shikar karta pakad ley, to wo uskey kapdey zabt kar ley.'' chunanche wo ghanimat jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey inayat farmaee hai wapis nahin karunga. haan agar chaho to uski qeemat dey deta hun."
2038,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik ghulam se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Madina ke kuchh ghulamon ko dekha ke wo (Haram) Madina mein darkht kaat rahey hain. to unhoney unka asbab chheen liya aur un ghulamon ke malikon se kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai ke aapney Madina ke darakhton se kuchh kaatney se mana farmaya hai. aur farmaya hai : ''jo koi in se kuchh kaatey to jo isey pakad ley to iska asbab usi ke liye hai (iskey kapdey, kulhaadii aur rassi waghaira).''"
2039,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke mehfooz karda ilaqey se na pattey todey jaeyn aur na darkht kaatey jaeyn magar halkey andaz mein pattey jhaad liye jaeyn.''"
2040,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qubaa tashrif ley jaya kartey they. kabhi paidal aur kabhi Sawar ho kar. ibne-Numair ne mazeed kaha : aur (masjid mein) do rakaten padha kartey they.
2041,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bhi mujhey salam kehta hai tu Allah mujh par meri rooh lauta deta hai aur main uskey salam ka jawab deta hun.''"
2042,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney gharon ko qabristaan mat banao. aur na meri qabr ko eid (mela gaah) banao aur mujh par durood padho. tum jahan kahin bhi hongey tumhara durood mujh ko pahunch jaeyga.''"
2043,"Rabeea bin Hudair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kabhi hadeese-Rasool bayan kartey nahin suna . magar eik hadees . shagrid ne kaha : maine puchha wo kaun si? (Talha ne) kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley , ham shahidon ki qabron ka qasad (irada) kiye huey they yahan tak ke ham Harra waqim par chadh gaey. jab is se nichey utrey to wahan eik janib mein qabren thin. ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya hamarey bhaiyon ki qabren yehi hain? aapney farmaya : ''ye hamarey as-haab ki qabren hain : ''phir jab ham shahidon ki qabron par pahunch gaey to farmaya : ''ye hamarey bhaiyon ki qabren hain.''"
2044,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zul-Hulaifa ke qarib Bat'haa (khuley maidan) main apni oontni bithaai aur wahan Namaz padhi. chunanche Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) is par amal kiya kartey they. (nichey likhi asar (qaul) mein iski wazahat hai.)
2045,(A) Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya : Madina wapis lautney waley ko layaq nahin ke maqame-muarris (Bat'haa masjid zul-hulaifa) se waisey hi guzar jaey. balke chahiye ke jis qadr dil chahey Namaz padhey kyonkey mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke aakhiri hissey mein yahan utartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke maine Muhammad bin Is'haq Madni se suna tha ke ''muarras'' Madina se chhe meel ke fasley par hai. (B) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ( Makka se Madina wapis ( aatey to maqame-muarris mein raat guzaartey yahan tak ke subah ko rawana hotey.
